Chinese (simplified): 一种远程可操纵的抛物面雷达天线，能够探测远距离的能量信号。\n[c][00FF00]主扫描(左键点击):[-][/c] 探测远距离的物体，但仅显示结果几秒钟。\n[c][00FF00]次级扫描(右键点击):[-][/c] 探测较短距离的物体，但持续时间更长。

English: A lightweight and compact shield generator design to ward off light armaments and meteorite impacts, but won't withstand heavy combat.\n[c][00BB00]Resists Kinetic weapons and Missiles, but susceptible to Lasers, Plasma and EMP.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种轻型且紧凑的护盾发生器设计，用于抵御轻型武器和陨石撞击，但无法承受重火力战斗。\n[c][00BB00]抵抗动能武器和导弹，但易受激光、等离子和电磁脉冲影响。[-][/c]

English: A lightweight and compact shield generator design to ward off light armaments and meteorite impacts, but won't withstand heavy combat.\n[c][00BB00]Resists Kinetic weapons and Missiles, but susceptible to Lasers, Plasma and EMP.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种轻型且紧凑的护盾发生器，设计用来抵御轻型武器和陨石撞击，但无法承受重火力战斗。\n[c][00BB00]抵御动能武器和导弹，但对激光、等离子和电磁脉冲敏感。[-][/c]

English: The upgraded version of the Standard Shield Generator. It can deflect almost any kinetic weapon with minimal energy expenditure and withstand direct strikes from heavy plasma weaponry.\n[c][00BB00]Resists Kinetic weapons and Missiles, but susceptible to Lasers, Plasma and EMP.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 标准护盾发生器的升级版本。它能够以最小的能量消耗偏转几乎所有的动能武器，并能承受重型等离子武器的直接打击。\n[c][00BB00]抵御动能武器和导弹，但对激光、等离子和电磁脉冲敏感。[-][/c]

English: A standard-issue Shield Generator designed to offer significant protection against kinetic and explosive impacts, but can be disrupted by energy-based weapons. Offers superior protection over the Compact Shield Generator.\n[c][00BB00]Resists Kinetic weapons and Missiles, but susceptible to Lasers, Plasma and EMP.[-][/c]
Deutsch: Ein standardmäßiger Schildgenerator, der erheblichen Schutz vor kinetischen und explosiven Einschlägen bietet, aber durch energiebasierte Waffen gestört werden kann. Bietet überlegenen Schutz gegenüber dem Compact Shield Generator.\n[c][00BB00]Widersteht kinetischen Waffen und Raketen, ist aber anfällig für Laser, Plasma und EMP.[-][/c]
Français: Un générateur de bouclier standard conçu pour offrir une protection significative contre les impacts cinétiques et explosifs, mais peut être perturbé par des armes à base d'énergie. Offre une protection supérieure par rapport au générateur de bouclier compact.\n[c][00BB00]Résiste aux armes cinétiques et aux missiles, mais sensible aux lasers, au plasma et aux EMP.[-][/c]
Italiano: Un generatore di scudi standard progettato per offrire una protezione significativa contro impatti cinetici ed esplosivi, ma può essere interrotto da armi a energia. Offre una protezione superiore rispetto al generatore di scudi compatti.\n[c][00BB00]Resiste alle armi cinetiche e ai missili, ma è sensibile a laser, plasma ed EMP.[-][/c]
Spanish: Un generador de escudo estándar diseñado para ofrecer una protección significativa contra impactos cinéticos y explosivos, pero que puede ser interrumpido por armas basadas en energía. Ofrece una protección superior al generador de escudo compacto.\n[c][00BB00]Resiste armas cinéticas y misiles, pero es susceptible a láseres, plasma y EMP.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种标准配发的护盾发生器，旨在提供显著的防护，抵御动能和爆炸性冲击，但可能会被基于能量的武器干扰。与紧凑型护盾发生器相比，提供更高级的保护。\n[c][00BB00]抵御动能武器和导弹，但对激光、等离子和电磁脉冲敏感。[-][/c]

English: A military-issue Shield Generator designed to offer superior protection against hostile attack over the Standard Shield Generator.\n[c][00BB00]Resists Kinetic weapons and Missiles, but susceptible to Lasers, Plasma and EMP.\n[-][/c]
Deutsch: Ein militärischer Schildgenerator, der überlegenen Schutz vor feindlichen Angriffen gegenüber dem Standard-Schildgenerator bietet.\n[c][00BB00]Widersteht kinetischen Waffen und Raketen, ist aber anfällig für Laser, Plasma und EMP.\n[-][/c]
Français: Un générateur de bouclier militaire conçu pour offrir une protection supérieure contre les attaques hostiles par rapport au générateur de bouclier standard.\n[c][00BB00]Résiste aux armes cinétiques et aux missiles, mais sensible aux lasers, au plasma et aux EMP.\n[-][/c]
Italiano: Un generatore di scudi di emissione militare progettato per offrire una protezione superiore contro gli attacchi ostili rispetto al generatore di scudi standard.\n[c][00BB00]Resiste alle armi cinetiche e ai missili, ma è sensibile a laser, plasma ed EMP.\n[-][/c]
Spanish: Un generador de escudo militar diseñado para ofrecer una protección superior contra ataques hostiles sobre el generador de escudo estándar.\n[c][00BB00]Resiste armas cinéticas y misiles, pero es susceptible a láseres, plasma y EMP.\n[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种军用护盾发生器，旨在提供比标准护盾发生器更高级的防护以抵御敌对攻击。\n[c][00BB00]抵御动能武器和导弹，但对激光、等离子和电磁脉冲敏感。[-][/c]

English: [c][00FF00]Increases Maximum CPU Limit[-][/c]\nSome form of computing hardware that appears to have originated from The Legacy. Although it seemingly has no limits, you should use with caution.\n[c][FF0000]The possession and use of Legacy Technology is forbidden under Galactic Law due to its corruptive nature.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): [c][00FF00]增加最大CPU限制[-][/c]\n一种计算硬件，似乎起源于“遗留者”。尽管它看起来没有限制，但你应该谨慎使用。\n[c][FF0000]根据银河法律，由于其腐化性质，拥有和使用遗留技术是被禁止的。[-][/c]

English: [sup]A repurposed Disruptor Cannon extracted from the remains of a Legacy ship's internal autofactory. While not as powerful as a Legacy-controlled turret, it is still capable of dealing catastrophic damage to armor and weapon, though lacks the ability to penetrate shields.[/sup]\n[c][FF0000]Low Damage vs Energy Shields[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]The possession and use of Legacy Technology is forbidden under Galactic Law due to its corruptive nature.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): [sup]一种重新利用的破坏者炮，从一艘遗留者飞船的内部自动工厂中提取出来。虽然它没有遗留者控制的炮台那么强大，但它仍然能够对装甲和武器造成灾难性的伤害，尽管它没有穿透护盾的能力。[/sup]\n[c][FF0000]对能量护盾的伤害低[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]根据银河法律，由于其腐化性质，拥有和使用遗留技术是被禁止的。[-][/c]

English: A ship-mounted Beam Cutter and Welder designed for the quick and precise salvage of space wrecks and the repair of surface damage. Although lacking the ability to accurately retrieve structural parts, it was deemed unnecessary since the sheer mass would render any ship immobile.\n[c][FF0000]Can Repair and Salvage Blocks (75% Salvage Rate)[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种舰载的光束切割器和焊接器，专为快速准确地打捞太空残骸和修复表面损伤而设计。尽管缺乏准确回收结构部件的能力，但人们认为这是不必要的，因为其巨大的质量会使任何飞船无法移动。\n[c][FF0000]可以修复和打捞区块(75%的打捞率)[-][/c]

English: A large-sized Cargo Container with logistics connectivity.\n[c][FFFFFF]Size:[-][/c] 4x4x4
Chinese (simplified): 一种大型货物集装箱，具有物流连接性。\n[c][FFFFFF]尺寸:[-][/c] 4x4x4

English: A large-sized Harvest Container with logistics connectivity into which anything harvested with a Drill, Multiturret or Harvest module will be deposited.\n[c][FFFFFF]Size:[-][/c] 4x4x4
Chinese (simplified): 一种大型收获集装箱，具有物流连接性，使用钻头、多管炮台或收获模块收获的任何物品都将被存放其中。\n[c][FFFFFF]尺寸:[-][/c] 4x4x4

English:
Light Armor provides protection from environmental and damage with an emphasis on mobility and functionality in everyday life.
Each suit includes a Jetpack (J), A headlight (L) and Oxygen Tanks.

[c][00FF00]Light Armor can be equipped from your Inventory but an Armor Locker is required to modify this suit.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
轻型护甲提供针对环境和伤害的保护，强调在日常生活中的机动性和功能性。
每套护甲包括一个喷气背包 (J)、一个头灯 (L) 和氧气罐。

[c][00FF00]轻型护甲可以从你的库存中装备，但需要护甲柜来修改这套护甲。[-][/c]

English:
Medium Armor provides good protection from the environment and damage with a good balance between mobility and defense, but doesn't excel in either aspect.
Includes a Jetpack (J), A headlight (L) and Oxygen Tanks.

[c][00FF00]An Armor Locker is required to equip or modify this suit.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
中型护甲在环境和伤害保护方面提供良好的防护，兼顾了机动性和防御性，但在任何一方面都不突出。
包括一个喷气背包 (J)、一个头灯 (L) 和氧气罐。

[c][00FF00]需要一个护甲柜来装备或修改这套护甲。[-][/c]

English:
Heavy Armor restricts mobility and oxygen capacity with denser plating in favor of unsurpassed protection from damage.
Includes a Jetpack (J), A headlight (L) and Oxygen.

[c][00FF00]An Armor Locker is required to equip or modify this suit.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
重型护甲在提供无与伦比的伤害保护的同时，限制了机动性和氧气容量，采用更密集的装甲板。
包括一个喷气背包 (J)、一个头灯 (L) 和氧气。

[c][00FF00]需要一个护甲柜来装备或修改这套护甲。[-][/c]

English:
Improved Light Armor is an upgraded version of the standard Light Armor. Providing additional carrying capacity, durability and an additional Booster Slot.
Light armor emphasizes mobility and functionality in everyday life over damage protection.

[c][00FF00]Light Armors can be equipped from your Inventory but an Armor Locker is required to modify this suit.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
改进型轻型护甲是标准轻型护甲的升级版。提供额外的携带能力、耐久度和一个额外的助推器插槽。
轻型护甲强调在日常生活中的机动性和功能性，而不是伤害保护。

[c][00FF00]轻型护甲可以从你的库存中装备，但需要护甲柜来修改这套护甲。[-][/c]

English:
Improved Medium Armor is an upgraded version of the standard Medium Armor. It provides increased carrying capacity, durability and an additional Booster Slot.
Medium armors emphasize on a balanced performance between mobility and damage protection, but doesn't excel in either aspect.

[c][00FF00]An Armor Locker is required to equip or modify this suit.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
改进型中型护甲是标准中型护甲的升级版。它提供了增加的携带能力、耐久度和一个额外的助推器插槽。
中型护甲强调在机动性和伤害保护之间平衡性能，但在任何一方面都不突出。

[c][00FF00]需要一个护甲柜来装备或修改这套护甲。[-][/c]

English:
Improved Heavy Armor is an upgraded version of the standard Heavy Armor that provides increased carrying capacity, durability and an additional Booster Slot
The armor is still restrictive and bulky but provides unsurpassed protection from combat damage at the cost of mobility and oxygen tank size.

[c][00FF00]An Armor Locker is required to equip or modify this suit.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
改进型重型护甲是标准重型护甲的升级版，提供增加的携带能力、耐久度和一个额外的助推器插槽。
护甲仍然具有限制性且体积庞大，但在提供无与伦比的战斗伤害保护的同时，牺牲了机动性和氧气罐的容量。

[c][00FF00]需要一个护甲柜来装备或修改这套护甲。[-][/c]

English:
Advanced Light Armor is the latest design in lightweight protection. Providing the maximum in carrying capacity, durability and full Booster Slots.
Light armor emphasizes mobility and functionality in everyday life over damage protection.

[c][00FF00]Light Armors can be equipped from your Inventory but an Armor Locker is required to modify this suit.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
先进的轻型护甲是轻量级保护的最新设计。提供最大的携带能力、耐久度和完整的助推器插槽。
轻型护甲强调在日常生活中的机动性和功能性，而不是伤害保护。

[c][00FF00]轻型护甲可以从你的库存中装备，但需要护甲柜来修改这套护甲。[-][/c]

English:
Advanced Medium Armor is the latest design in balanced, all-round protection. Providing the maximum in carrying capacity, durability and full Booster Slots.
Medium armors emphasize on a balanced performance between mobility and damage protection, but doesn't excel in either aspect.

[c][00FF00]An Armor Locker is required to equip or modify this suit.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
先进的中型护甲是平衡全面保护的最新设计。提供最大的携带能力、耐久度和全部助推器插槽。
中型护甲强调在机动性和伤害保护之间平衡性能，但在任何一方面都不突出。

[c][00FF00]需要一个护甲柜来装备或修改这套护甲。[-][/c]

English:
Advanced Heavy Armor is the latest design in combat-ready apparel that provides the maximum in carrying capacity, durability and full Booster Slots.
With unsurpassed protection from weapons fire the drawbacks of poor mobility and oxygen tank size can be modded out.

[c][00FF00]An Armor Locker is required to equip or modify this suit.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
先进的重型护甲是战斗准备服装的最新设计，提供最大的携带能力、耐久度和全部助推器插槽。
具有无与伦比的防护能力，可以抵御武器火力，其缺点是机动性差和氧气罐容量小，但这些可以通过改装来改善。

[c][00FF00]需要一个护甲柜来装备或修改这套护甲。[-][/c]

English:
Standard Light Armor customized with an AI Control Unit that can house IDA's Core, augmenting the suit's abilities with added processing power.
Functionally identical to Light Armor, but the added AI module provides additional radiation shielding and heating.

[c][00FF00]Light Armors can be equipped from your Inventory but an Armor Locker is required to modify this suit.[-][/c]
[c][FFE100]Mission Item[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
标准轻型护甲配备有AI控制单元，可以容纳IDA的核心，通过增加处理能力增强护甲的功能。
在功能上与轻型护甲相同，但增加的AI模块提供额外的辐射屏蔽和隔热。

[c][00FF00]轻型护甲可以从你的库存中装备，但需要护甲柜来修改这套护甲。[-][/c]
[c][FFE100]任务物品[-][/c]

English: A coolant-lined superconducting cable made from a highly-refined Zascosium alloy mix designed to transfer power with zero transmission loss at the maximum possible speed.
Chinese (simplified): 一种由高度精炼的铡合金混合物制成的冷却液衬里超导电缆，设计用于以在最大可能速度下零损失地传输电力。

English: A Sathium-reinforced composite plating comprised of several layers of different materials with varying radioactive modulus that's used on commercial warp drives and fusion reactors.
Chinese (simplified): 一种钑增强复合装甲板，由多层不同材料组成，具有不同的放射性模量，用于商业翘曲驱动器和聚变反应堆。

English: A carbon-fluorine superfluid is sealed inside the microscopic pores of each cell that maximizes energy capture and attenuation.\nUsed in the production of high-quality solar panels and satellites.
Chinese (simplified): 一种碳-氟超流体被密封在每个单元的微观孔隙中，最大化能量捕获和衰减。\n用于生产高质量的太阳能板和卫星。

English: Drive thruster components used in the production of engines on long-haul freighters and battleships that are subject to higher stresses than normal thrusters.
Chinese (simplified): 驱动推进器部件，用于生产长途货船和战舰上的发动机，这些发动机比普通推进器承受更高的压力。

English: A stable, crystalline form of carbon that possesses good conductive properties among others. It's both a precursor to industrial diamond production and the manufacture of graphene nanofiber material in high-end electronics.
Deutsch: Eine stabile, kristalline Form von Kohlenstoff, die unter anderem gute Leitfähigkeitseigenschaften besitzt. Es ist sowohl ein Vorläufer der industriellen Diamantproduktion als auch der Hersteller von Graphen-Nanofasermaterial in der High-End-Elektronik.
Français: Une forme stable et cristalline de carbone qui possède entre autres de bonnes propriétés conductrices. C'est à la fois un précurseur de la production industrielle de diamants et le fabricant de nanofibres de graphène dans l'électronique haut de gamme.
Italiano: Una forma stabile e cristallina di carbonio che possiede, tra le altre, buone proprietà conduttive. È sia un precursore della produzione industriale di diamanti che il produttore di materiale in nanofibra di grafene nell'elettronica di fascia alta.
Spanish: Una forma de carbono estable y cristalina que posee, entre otras, buenas propiedades conductoras. Es tanto un precursor de la producción industrial de diamantes como el fabricante de material de nanofibras de grafeno en la electrónica de alta gama.
Chinese (simplified): 一种稳定的、结晶形式的碳，具有良好的导电性等特性。它既是工业钻石生产的前体，也是高端电子产品中石墨烯纳米纤维材料的制造材料。

English: A common and vital element used in everything from explosives to medical ingredients.\nAlthough common, it is always in demand throughout the galactic market.
Deutsch: Ein übliches und lebenswichtiges Element, das in allem verwendet wird, von Sprengstoffen bis hin zu medizinischen Inhaltsstoffen.\nObwohl es üblich ist, wird es immer auf dem gesamten galaktischen Markt nachgefragt.
Français: Un élément commun et vital utilisé dans tout, des explosifs aux ingrédients médicaux.\nBien que commun, il est toujours demandé sur tout le marché galactique.
Italiano: Un elemento comune e vitale utilizzato in tutto, dagli esplosivi agli ingredienti medici.\nAnche se comune, è sempre richiesto in tutto il mercato galattico.
Spanish: Un elemento común y vital que se usa en todo, desde explosivos hasta ingredientes médicos.\nAunque es común, siempre está en demanda en todo el mercado galáctico.
Chinese (simplified): 一种常见且至关重要的元素，用于从爆炸物到医疗成分的所有领域。\n尽管常见，但在整个银河市场中始终有需求。

English: Flat-packed Prefab Housing modules commonly used in the wake of environmental disasters or during the construction period of outlying colonies.\nThey're not the most spacious or comfortable, but it's better than a tent.
Chinese (simplified): 平板预制房屋模块，通常用于环境灾难后或边远殖民地建设期间。\n它们不是最宽敞或舒适的，但总比帐篷好。

English: The core module of a Fusion Reactor that contains not only the reaction chamber but the feed lines for the fuel, with enough shielding and coolant channels for use in compact generators.
Chinese (simplified): 一个聚变反应堆的核心模块，不仅包含反应室，还有燃料的供给线，有足够的屏蔽和冷却通道，适用于紧凑型发电机。

English: Unknown electronic components that comprise the inner workings of quantum computers. The technology is formulated at the picoscopic level up, making it impossible to replicate or even understand.
Chinese (simplified): 未知的电子组件，构成量子计算机的内部运作。该技术从微观层面上制定，使其无法复制或甚至理解。

English: An aluminium-palladium heat sink used to draw heat away from vital components and either disperse it or dump it into external coolant systems.
Chinese (simplified): 一种铝钯散热器，用于将热量从关键组件中吸走，然后将其分散或排入外部冷却系统。

English: An essential mineral used in everything from food to agriculture and numerous industrial applications.\nAlthough not particularly valuable, it is always in demand throughout the galactic market.
Deutsch: Ein essentielles Mineral, das in allem von der Nahrung über die Landwirtschaft bis hin zu zahlreichen industriellen Anwendungen verwendet wird.\nObwohl es nicht besonders wertvoll ist, ist es auf dem gesamten galaktischen Markt immer gefragt.
Français: Un minéral essentiel utilisé dans tout, de l'alimentation à l'agriculture et dans de nombreuses applications industrielles.\nBien qu'il ne soit pas particulièrement précieux, il est toujours en demande sur tout le marché galactique.
Italiano: Un minerale essenziale utilizzato in tutto, dal cibo all'agricoltura e in numerose applicazioni industriali.\nAnche se non particolarmente prezioso, è sempre richiesto in tutto il mercato galattico.
Spanish: Un mineral esencial que se utiliza en todo, desde la alimentación hasta la agricultura y numerosas aplicaciones industriales.\nAunque no es particularmente valioso, siempre tiene una demanda en todo el mercado galáctico.
Chinese (simplified): 一种必需的矿物，用于从食品到农业和许多工业应用的所有领域。\n尽管不是特别有价值，但在整个银河市场中始终有需求。

English: A packed and sealed case with standard equipment used by outlying colonies and mining rigs to extract resources from deep underground, beneath the bedrock layers.
Chinese (simplified): 一个装满并密封的标准设备箱，由边远殖民地和采矿设备用来从地下深处、基岩层以下提取资源。

English: A pressurized bottle of compressed helium typically used as fuel for low-yield Fusion Reactors and some older model thrusters that require propellant.
Chinese (simplified): 一瓶压缩氦气，通常用作低产聚变反应堆的燃料，以及一些需要推进剂的旧型号推进器。

English: A pressurized bottle of liquid nitrogen, reinforced against the extreme cold of the fluid. It can be used to produce starship coolant and as a chemical agent in the use of fertilizers and explosives.
Chinese (simplified): 一瓶加压的液态氮，加固以抵抗流体的极端寒冷。它可以用于生产星际飞船冷却剂，并作为肥料和爆炸物的化学剂。

English: A pressurized bottle of compressed Xenon Gas used in laser production and precision machinery as well as several medical applications.
Chinese (simplified): 一瓶加压的氙气，用于激光生产、精密机械以及几种医疗应用。

English: A packed and sealed container of communication equipment used in the establishment of long-ranged communications with outlying colonies and deep space FTL coms.
Chinese (simplified): 一个装满并密封的通信设备容器，用于与边远殖民地和深空FTL通信建立远程通信。

English: The ZMX-404 is in simpler terms: A landmine.\nThe construction is fundamentally similar to UCH munitions of the same class but contains an electronic safety that reacts only to zirax bio-signatures. This is renders the weapon useless if stolen since it cannot be repurposed easily.
Chinese (simplified): ZMX-404简单来说是一种地雷。\n其构造基本上与UCH同类弹药相似，但包含一个电子安全装置，仅对兹瑞克斯生物特征反应。这使得武器如果被盗则无法轻易重新利用，因而变得无用。

English: Standard data extracted from a "secure" system that can be data-mined for sensitive information concerning civilian work orders, ship maintenance and economic data.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Can be sold to an Information Broker on some stations
Deutsch: Standarddaten, die aus einem "sicheren" System extrahiert werden, das nach sensiblen Informationen zu zivilen Arbeitsaufträgen, Schiffswartung und Wirtschaftsdaten durchsucht werden kann.\n\n[c][FFBB00]Kann an einigen Stationen an einen Informationsmakler verkauft werden

English: Unstable, supersatured polycrystal of Pentaxium. If placed in a hydroponics unit with a supply of mineral solution it will grow and form larger crystals of Pentaxid.\n[c][FF00FF]Radioactive and Volatile. Drains power from structure grid while growing.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 不稳定的超饱和多晶翘曲晶体。如果放置在有矿物质溶液供应的水培单元中，它将生长并形成更大的翘曲晶体。\n[c][FF00FF]放射性和易挥发。生长时需要消耗电能。[-][/c]

English: [c][b][FFBB00]DEHYDRATION[-][/b][/c]\nYou are dehydrated!\n[c][FFFFFF]Replenish your fluids by drinking water, juice or tea[-][/c]
Deutsch: Sie sind dehydriert!\nFüllen Sie Ihre Flüssigkeit durch Wasser, Saft oder Tee wieder auf!
Français: Vous êtes déshydraté!\nFaites le plein en buvant de l'eau, du jus ou du thé!
Italiano: Sei disidratato!\nRifornisci i tuoi liquidi bevendo acqua, succhi di frutta o tè!
Spanish: ¡Estás deshidratado!\n¡Repone tus líquidos bebiendo agua, jugo o té!
Chinese (simplified): [b][c][FFBB00]脱水[-][/c][/b]\n你脱水了！[c][FFFFFF]\n通过喝水、果汁或茶来补充你的水分[-][/c]

English: You have been poisoned!\nThe poison has spread through your body and can only be treated with Antitoxic Pills, Injections or a Detox Kit
Deutsch: Sie wurden vergiftet!\nDas Gift hat sich in Ihrem Körper ausgebreitet und kann nur mit antitoxischen Pillen, Injektionen oder einem Detox-Kit behandelt werden
Français: Vous avez été empoisonné !\nLe poison s'est propagé dans votre corps et ne peut être traité qu'avec des pilules antitoxiques, des injections ou un kit de désintoxication
Italiano: Sei stato avvelenato!\nIl veleno si è diffuso nel tuo corpo e può essere trattato solo con pillole antitossiche, iniezioni o un kit disintossicante
Spanish: ¡Te han envenenado!\nEl veneno se ha esparcido por tu cuerpo y solo se puede tratar con píldoras antitóxicas, inyecciones o un kit de desintoxicación.
Chinese (simplified): 你中毒了！毒素已经遍布你的全身，只能用抗毒药片、注射剂或解毒医疗包来治疗。

English: Antibiotic salve that's applied topically to the affected area to seal and treat dermal burns and restore bloodflow to frostbitten tissue.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 抗生素软膏，局部应用于受影响区域，以封闭和治疗皮肤烧伤，恢复冻伤组织血流。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]使用工具栏中的左键点击或从库存中使用Shift+右键点击[-][/c]

English: Broad-spectrum antibiotic pills used to treat a variety of systemic infections.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 广谱抗生素药片，用于治疗多种系统性感染。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]使用工具栏中的左键点击(LMB)或从库存中使用Shift+右键点击(RMB)[-][/c]

English: A high-strength Antibiotic Injector formulated for use against severe bacterial infections like Septicemia and Gangrene before they turn fatal.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种高强度的抗生素注射器，专为治疗严重的细菌感染如败血症和坏疽而配制，以防它们变得致命。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]使用工具栏中的左键点击(LMB)或从库存中使用Shift+右键点击(RMB)[-][/c]

English:
A topical treatment for Radiation Burns designed to purge residual radiation from fatty tissue.
[c][00FFAA]Does NOT purge radiation from the body. Unless the radiation is removed by Decontamination or a Shower, symptoms may reappear.[-][/c]

[c][FFFFFF]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种用于治疗辐射烧伤的外用药物，旨在从脂肪组织中清除残留的辐射。
[c][00FFAA]不从体内清除辐射。除非通过去污或淋浴去除辐射，否则症状可能会重新出现。[-][/c]

[c][FFFFFF]使用工具栏中的左键点击(LMB)或从库存中使用Shift+右键点击(RMB)[-][/c]

English:
A formulated medical treatment using Iodine nano-particles for acute radiation exposue and subsequent Radiation Poisoning.
[c][00FFAA]Does NOT purge radiation from the body. Unless the radiation is removed by Decontamination or a Shower, symptoms may reoccur.[-][/c]

[c][FFFFFF]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种使用碘纳米粒子制定的医疗治疗方法，用于急性辐射暴露和随后的辐射中毒。
[c][00FFAA]不从体内清除辐射。除非通过去污或淋浴去除辐射，否则症状可能会再次发生。[-][/c]

[c][FFFFFF]使用工具栏中的左键点击(LMB)或从库存中使用Shift+右键点击(RMB)[-][/c]

English: High-strength medical treatment for food poisoning, indigestion, period pain and stomach cramps. If symptoms persist, see a doctor.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 高强度的医疗治疗，用于食物中毒、消化不良、痛经和胃痉挛。如果症状持续，请看医生。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]使用工具栏中的左键点击(LMB)或从库存中使用Shift+右键点击(RMB)[-][/c]

English: A unique medication used for filtering toxins, venom and harmful contaminants from the patient's blood without any adverse effects. Recommended for swamp and jungle environments where venomous creatures are common.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种独特的药物，用于过滤患者血液中的毒素、蛇毒和有害物质，没有任何副作用。推荐在沼泽和丛林环境中使用，这些地方常见的有毒生物。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]使用工具栏中的左键点击(LMB)或从库存中使用Shift+右键点击(RMB)[-][/c]

English: A complex anti-toxicity injection applied directly into the chest muscles, it counteracts numerous internal conditions by cleaning out build-ups of toxins and impurities in the blood typically caused by Kidney or Liver failure.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种复杂的抗毒性注射剂，直接注射到胸肌中，它通过清除血液中由肾脏或肝脏衰竭引起的毒素和杂质积累，对抗许多内部疾病。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]使用工具栏中的左键点击(LMB)或从库存中使用Shift+右键点击(RMB)[-][/c]

English: Extra-Large structural armor blocks used to produce elongated armor shapes made of steel.
Chinese (simplified): 超大型结构装甲方块，用于制作钢制的延长型护甲形状。

English: Extra-Large structural armor blocks used to produce elongated armor shapes made of Titanium Alloy
Chinese (simplified): 超大型结构装甲方块，用于制作钛合金制的延长型护甲形状。

English: Extra-Large structural armor blocks used to produce elongated armor shapes made of Sathium Alloy.
Chinese (simplified): 超大型结构装甲方块，用于制作钑合金制的延长型护甲形状。

English: A high-value Platinum Credit Card issued by Trade Federation Banking. Each credit represents a total sum of 10,000 Credits that can be deposited into an ATM.\nMost businesses do not accept Platinum Credit.
Chinese (simplified): 由贸易联盟银行发行的高价值白金信用卡。每张信用卡代表可以在自动取款机存入的总计10,000信用点。\n大多数企业不接受白金信用卡。

English: Security Contract for a single security guard for static structures.\nPlaces the crewmember's bed from which they will be deployed.\nWill patrol the area and engage hostile targets.
Chinese (simplified): 单个静态结构的安保人员的安保合同。\n放置船员的床，他们将从这里被部署。\n将巡逻区域并与敌对目标交战。

English: A portable Security Android for static structures.\nPlaces the android's charging pad from which they will be deployed.\nWill patrol the area and engage hostile targets.
Chinese (simplified): 一种用于静态结构的便携式安保机器人。\n放置机器人的充电垫，他们将从这里被部署。\n将巡逻区域并与敌对目标交战。

English: A Type-22 Deployable Heavy Mechanoid for militarized structures.\nPlaces the Mechanoid's charging pad from which they will be deployed.\nWill patrol the area and engage hostile targets.
Chinese (simplified): 一种用于军事化结构的22型可部署重型机械人。\n放置机械人的充电垫，他们将从这里被部署。\n将巡逻区域并与敌对目标交战。

English: A secondary capacitor dedicated to supplying reserve energy to a shield generator; increasing shield strength at the cost of shield charge speed.\n[c][00FF00]Increases Shield Capacity[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Reduces Shield Charge Rate[-][/c]
Deutsch: Ein Sekundärkondensator, der dazu bestimmt ist, einen Schildgenerator mit Reserveenergie zu versorgen; Erhöhung der Schildstärke auf Kosten der Schildladegeschwindigkeit.
Français: Un condensateur secondaire dédié à la fourniture d'énergie de réserve à un générateur de bouclier ; augmenter la force du bouclier au détriment de la vitesse de charge du bouclier.
Italiano: Un condensatore secondario dedicato a fornire energia di riserva a un generatore di schermatura; aumentando la forza dello scudo a scapito della velocità di carica dello scudo.
Spanish: Un condensador secundario dedicado a suministrar energía de reserva a un generador de pantalla; aumentando la fuerza del escudo a costa de la velocidad de carga del escudo.
Chinese (simplified): 一个专用于向护盾发生器提供储备能量的辅助电容；以牺牲护盾充电速度为代价增加护盾强度。\n[c][00FF00]增加护盾容量[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]降低护盾充电速率[-][/c]

English: A large auxillary capacitor bank used in larger vessels dedicated to supplying additional energy to a shield generator; increasing shield strength at the cost of shield charge speed.\n[c][00FF00]Increases Shield Capacity[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Reduces Shield Charge Rate[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一个大型辅助电容器组，用于在较大的飞船中向护盾发生器提供额外能量；以牺牲护盾充电速度为代价增加护盾强度。\n[c][00FF00]增加护盾容量[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]降低护盾充电速率[-][/c]

English: A primary capacitor that subsumes the role of a battleship's main power storage for shield generation; increasing shield strength at the cost of shield charge speed.\n[c][00FF00]Increases Shield Capacity[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Reduces Shield Charge Rate[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一个主要电容器，承担了战列舰主要电源存储的角色，用于护盾生成；以牺牲护盾充电速度为代价增加护盾强度。

[c][00FF00]增加护盾容量[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]降低护盾充电速率[-][/c]

English: A main power coupling and regulator that diverts higher charge to a shield generator; increasing shield charge speed at the cost of shield strength.\n[c][00FF00]Increases Shield Charge Rate[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Reduces Shield Capacity[-][/c]
Deutsch: Eine Hauptstromkopplung und ein Regler, der höhere Ladung zu einem Schildgenerator umleitet; Erhöhung der Schildladegeschwindigkeit auf Kosten der Schildstärke.
Français: Un couplage et un régulateur d'alimentation principaux qui détournent une charge plus élevée vers un générateur de bouclier ; augmenter la vitesse de charge du bouclier au détriment de la force du bouclier.
Italiano: Un accoppiamento e un regolatore di alimentazione principale che devia una carica maggiore a un generatore di schermatura; aumentando la velocità di carica dello scudo a scapito della forza dello scudo.
Spanish: Un regulador y un acoplamiento de potencia principal que desvía una carga más alta a un generador de escudo; aumentando la velocidad de carga del escudo a costa de la fuerza del escudo.
Chinese (simplified):
一个主电源耦合器和调节器，将更高的电荷转移到护盾发生器；以牺牲护盾强度为代价增加护盾充电速度。

[c][00FF00]增加护盾充电速率[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]减少护盾容量[-][/c]

English: An auxillary power coupling with tremendous throughput that diverts higher charge to a shield generator; increasing shield charge speed at the cost of shield strength.\n[c][00FF00]Increases Shield Charge Rate[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Reduces Shield Capacity[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一个具有巨大吞吐量的辅助电源耦合器，将更多的电荷转移到护盾发生器；以牺牲护盾强度为代价提高护盾充电速度。

[c][00FF00]增加护盾充电速率[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]减少护盾容量[-][/c]

English: The primary energy conduit outfitted with superconductors used for supplying power from a Battleship's generators to the shield capacitors; increasing shield charge speed at the cost of shield strength.\n[c][00FF00]Increases Shield Charge Rate[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Reduces Shield Capacity[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
主要能量输送管道，配备了超导体，用于从战列舰的发电机向护盾电容器供电；以牺牲护盾强度为代价提高护盾充电速度。

[c][00FF00]增加护盾充电速率[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]减少护盾容量[-][/c]

English: A reconfigurable Shield Boosting Module capable of either increasing shield capacity [c][00FF00](Shield Capacitor)[-][/c] or shield charge rate [c][66CCFF](Shield Charger)[-][/c] at the cost of its opposing trait.\n[c][00FF00]Press RMB to see all available options[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一个可重新配置的护盾增强模块，能够增加护盾容量[c][00FF00](护盾电容器)[-][/c]或护盾充电速率[c][66CCFF](护盾充电器)[-][/c]，以牺牲其相对的特性为代价。\n[c][00FF00]点击鼠标右键查看所有可用选项[-][/c]

English: A Biofuel-powered mechanical drill used for mining rocks, terrain and ores faster than the Survival Multitool.\n[c][FFBB00]A dedicated mining vessel is recommended for extensive mining over reliance on hand tools.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种由生物燃料驱动的机械钻，用于比生存多用途工具更快地开采岩石、地形和矿石。\n[c][FFBB00]推荐使用专门的采矿船进行广泛采矿，而不是依赖手工工具。[-][/c]

English: A unique application of quantum tunnelling to fold space that allows more internal space than the dimensions of the container would allow.\n\n[c][F300FF]Quantum Technology[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 利用量子隧道效应的独特应用，可以折叠空间，使内部空间比容器的尺寸所允许的更多。\n\n[c][F300FF]量子技术[-][/c]

English: An atmospheric field designed to keep oxygen contained in an open and exposed space without the need for walls or door.\n[c][FF0000]Provides NO protection from weaponfire[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种旨在保持开放和暴露的空间氧气不流失，而不需求墙壁或门的大气场。\n[c][FF0000]对武器火力不提供任何保护[-][/c]

English: Ion Thrusters are the standard method of low-power propulsion.\nRadioactive waste from the ship's generators is ionized and propelled through an electromagnetic conductor to produce thrust.
Chinese (simplified): 离子推进器是低功率推进的标准方法。\n船上发电机的放射性废物被电离并通过电磁导体推进以产生推力。

English: Plasma Thrusters are most commonly used in military and compact vessels over cheaper alternatives.\nInternal plasma converters use the waste from the generator's output in a fissile reaction to produce a ring of magnetically-confined superheated plasma.
Chinese (simplified): 等离子体推进器通常在军事和紧凑型飞船中最常用，比更便宜的替代品更常见。\n内部等离子体转换器使用发电机输出的废物进行裂变反应，产生一个被磁约束的超热等离子体环。

English: Antimatter Thrusters are a revolution in propulsion technology that produce the highest thrust to weight presently possible.\nRadioactive particles from the ship's energy system are converted into antimatter using miniaturized particle accelerators and applied to waste gases in a reaction chamber to produce explosive thrust.
Chinese (simplified): 反物质推进器是推进技术的革命，产生目前可能的最高推力重量比。\n船上能量系统的放射性粒子通过小型化粒子加速器转换成反物质，并在反应室中应用于废气以产生爆炸性推力。

English: An improvement over the standard Jump Drive that allows the drive greater calculation capabilities without increasing it's size, allowing a smaller craft the ability to initiate interstellar jumps within limitations.
Chinese (simplified): 一种对标准跳跃驱动的改进，允许驱动器在不增加其尺寸的情况下具有更大的计算能力，使更小的飞船能够在限制范围内启动星际跳跃。

English: Enhanced conductance coils and better processing speed allows this Advanced Warp Drive the ability to jump further with much greater efficiency than it's standard counterpart.
Chinese (simplified): 增强的导电线圈和更好的处理速度使这种先进的翘曲驱动器能够比其标准对应物更有效地跳得更远。

English: As the name suggests, the Deconstructor's purpose is to take blocks and devices and disassemble them at 100% efficiency into their components.\nIt is not capable of dismantling components into raw ingots though.
Chinese (simplified): 顾名思义，解构器的目的是将方块和设备以100%的效率拆解成它们的组件。\n不过，它不能将组件拆解成原材料。

English: A state-of-the-art miniaturized fusion powerplant that can supply more power than any smaller craft present can draw. Much like its larger counterparts, it's intended for active use and will divert a small portion of its output to sustain a fusion reaction.
Chinese (simplified): 一种最先进的微型聚变发电厂，可以提供超过任何现有小型飞船所能抽取的电力。像它的大型对应物一样，它旨在积极使用，并将一小部分输出转向以维持聚变反应。

English:
Plasma Turbines are used as secondary power generation to recycle the waste plasma from a ship's Generators or Fusion Reactor to produce additional power.
[c][00FFFF]Plasma Turbines do not consume fuel
Each active turbine improves fuel efficiency by reducing a ship's energy consumption[-][/c]
[c][00FF00]Consumption: -200w.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
等离子涡轮机被用作次要的发电方式，通过回收飞船发电机或聚变反应堆产生的废料等离子体来产生额外的电力。
[c][00FFFF]等离子涡轮机不消耗燃料
每个活跃的涡轮机通过减少能源消耗来提高燃料效率[-][/c]
[c][00FF00]消耗:-200w。[-][/c]

English:
Plasma Turbines are used as secondary power generation to recycle the waste plasma from a ship's Generators or Fusion Reactor to produce additional power.
[c][00FFFF]Plasma Turbines do not consume fuel
Each active turbine improves fuel efficiency by reducing a ship's energy consumption[-][/c]
[c][00FF00]Consumption: -600w.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
等离子涡轮机被用作次要的发电方式，通过回收飞船的发电机或聚变反应堆产生的废料等离子体来产生额外的电力。
[c][00FFFF]等离子涡轮机不消耗燃料
每个活跃的涡轮机通过减少飞船的能源消耗来提高燃料效率[-][/c]
[c][00FF00]消耗:-600w。[-][/c]

English:
Plasma Turbines are used as secondary power generation to recycle the waste plasma from a ship's Generators or Fusion Reactor to produce additional power.

English: A Generator that operates by fusing two or more elements together to release massive amounts of energy.\nRequires a constant energy input to keep the reaction stable, making it suitable for high-output spacecrafts.

English: A shield generator intended for planetary installations.\nThis shield produces a spherical bubble not suitable for space and takes half damage from CV weapons.

English: A shield generator based on alien technology.\nGenerates a dome-shaped shield of plasma held in place by an EM field that consumes less pentaxid and power than other shield generators.
