一种利用外星技术增强效果的实验性等离子电池，其效果超越了这个星系以前所见的任何事物。

[c][00FF00]+25% 对装甲块的爆炸伤害提高
+40% 爆炸半径
-50% 装填时间减少[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]无冲击伤害[-][/c]
[c][FF00FF]40,000 护盾伤害每分钟[-][/c]

English: A type of capacitor that contains both a large amount of energy and an unstable isotope of Pentaxium that can be converted into a multi-phase wave of positrons. An antimatter particle (Anti-Electron) that annihilates electron bonds from whatever it comes in contact with, causing rapid uncontrolled fission.\n[c][00FF00]Used as ammunition by Positron weaponry[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种电容器，包含大量能量和一个不稳定的翘曲晶体同位素，可以转换成多相正电子波。正电子是一种反物质粒子(反电子)，它与任何接触的物质中的电子键发生湮灭，导致快速不受控制的裂变。\n\n[c][00FF00]用作正电子武器的弹药[-][/c]

English:
[c][66CCFF]Block Group[-][/c]: RMB to Access
Positron Blaster Turret: Positron Accumulator
Heavy Plasma Turret: 200MJ Exotic Plasma Cells
[c][FFBB00]Heavy Weapon: High Damage vs Energy Shields[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][66CCFF]方块组[-][/c]:右键访问
正电子爆破炮塔:正电子积累器
重型等离子炮塔:200MJ 异质等离子电池
[c][FFBB00]重型武器:对能量护盾造成高伤害[-][/c]

English:
The BFC10K is an experimental plasma weapon that can only be fired from a static position. It uses alien technology in both the weapon and ammunition to deliver more power than any other plasma weapon.
[c][00FF00]+25% Blast Damage vs Armor Blocks
+40% Blast Radius
-50% Reload Time[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]No impact damage[-][/c]
[c][FF00FF]40,000 Shield Damage per minute[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
BFC10K是一种实验性等离子武器，只能在静止位置发射。它在武器和弹药中都使用了外星技术，以提供比其他任何等离子武器更强的火力。

[c][00FF00]+25% 对装甲块的爆炸伤害提高
+40% 爆炸半径
-50% 装填时间减少[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]无冲击伤害[-][/c]
[c][FF00FF]40,000 护盾伤害每分钟[-][/c]

English: The Lohengrin Positron Blaster Cannon is an experimental energy weapon that strips electrons from whatever matter the beam comes in contact with. Unlike the ship-mounted version, this cannon does not cause radiological atmospheric contamination.\n[c][FF0000]-33% Damage vs Xenosteel[-][/c]\n[c][FF00FF]40,000 Shield Damage per minute[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 罗兰正电子爆破炮是一种实验性能量武器，它能从光束接触到的任何物质中剥离电子。与舰载版本不同，这种炮不会导致大气的放射性污染。\n[c][FF0000]-33% 对异星钢的伤害[-][/c]\n[c][FF00FF]40,000 护盾伤害每分钟[-][/c]

English: [c][FF0000]POI Turret intended for planetary POIs ONLY![-][/c]\nThis turret inflicts 200% hull and shield damage to Capital Vessels and Bases in atmosphere to give HV/SV the advantage.
Chinese (simplified): [c][FF0000]POI炮塔，仅限于行星POI使用！[-][/c]\n该炮塔在大气中对首都舰船和基地造成200%的船体和护盾伤害，以给予HV/SV优势。

English: [c][FF0000]Advanced POI Turret intended for planetary POIs ONLY![-][/c]\nAn improvement over the standard turret, this dome-shaped turret has a more confined field of view, but with a superior damage output.\nThis turret inflicts 200% hull and shield damage to Capital Vessels and Bases in atmosphere to give HV/SV the advantage.
Chinese (simplified): [c][FF0000]高级POI炮塔，仅限于行星POI使用！[-][/c]\n作为标准炮塔的改进版，这种圆顶形状的炮塔拥有更狭窄的视场，但具有更优越的损害输出。\n该炮塔在大气中对首都舰船和基地造成200%的船体和护盾伤害，以提供给HV/SV优势。

English: A turret designed for operation on both planets and space without any significant loss in performance in either environment.
Chinese (simplified): 一种炮塔，旨在在行星和太空中操作，且在这两种环境中都不会有显著的性能损失。\n

English: An Advanced Turret with a naval dome design intended for operation on both planets and space without any significant loss in performance in either environment.\n Has a more confined fields of view, being unable to fire downward, but has a full range of movement vertically where standard models aren't able to aim.
Chinese (simplified): 一种采用海军穹顶设计的高级炮塔，旨在在行星和太空中操作，且在这两种环境中都不会有显著的性能损失。\n拥有更狭窄的视场，无法向下射击，但在垂直方向上有完全的运动范围，而标准型号则无法瞄准。

English: The pink meat of a cold water fish. Used in a number of local and foreign cuisines, it's quite valuable if you can get past the smell.
Chinese (simplified): 一种冷水鱼的粉红色鱼肉。如果能够忽略其气味，它在当地和外国的许多菜肴中都有使用，并且相当有价值。

English: A thruster reaction chamber module used to convert waste from a ship's generators into ionized gases to be used as propellant for increased thrust.\n\n[c][00FF00]Used to upgrade an Ion Thruster into a Plasma Thruster[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种推进器反应室模块，用于将飞船发电机的废物转化为离子气体，用作推进剂以增加推力。\n\n[c][00FF00]用于将离子推进器升级为等离子推进器[-][/c]

English: A dual ring-type particle accelerator encasing a reaction chamber where particles of radioactive waste from a ship's power system are collided to produce antimatter and channel the subsequent explosion as propulsion.\n\n[c][00FF00]Used to upgrade a Plasma Thruster into an Antimatter Thruster[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种双环型粒子加速器，包裹着一个反应室，其中飞船动力系统的放射性废物粒子被碰撞以产生反物质，并将随后的爆炸作为推进力。

[c][00FF00]用于将等离子推进器升级为反物质推进器[-][/c]

English: Packaged furniture designed to be mass-produced for low cost and high strength. Common in both the homes of laborers and colonists as well as the barracks of your local imperial base.
Chinese (simplified): 为低成本和高强度而设计的包装家具。它在劳工和殖民者的家中以及当地帝国基地的军营中都很常见。\n

English: Quality furniture designed with both an eye to detail and form. Comfortable and durable enough for everyday use, but heavy and not up to the rigors and abuses of a frontier settlement.
Chinese (simplified): 精心设计的高品质家具，注重细节和形态。舒适耐用，适合日常使用，但重量较重，不适合边疆定居点的艰苦和滥用。

English: Standard clothing that is often worn by civilians among the Trade Federation, Zirax Empire, Colonists and even Pirates.
Chinese (simplified): 贸易联盟、兹瑞克斯帝国、殖民者甚至海盗中平民常穿的标准服装。

English: Flexible and strong body armor designed for security personnel and paramilitary groups. It's resistant to a variety of weapons, but lacks the utility of a space suit or a suit constructor.
Chinese (simplified): 为安保人员和准军事团体设计的灵活且坚固的防弹衣。它对各种武器都有一定的抵抗力，但缺乏太空服或建造机服的实用性。

English: Strong and comfortable clothing worn by hands-on workers across the galaxy, from farmers to factory workers. It stands up to the rigors of daily life in the industrial sector.
Chinese (simplified): 从农民到工厂工人，全银河系的体力劳动者都穿着这种结实舒适的工作服。它能够承受工业领域日常生活的严峻考验。

English: Quality designer clothing of fine material and weave, typically worn by the rich and powerful across the galaxy but not uncommon in a civilian's wardrobe for important occasions.
Chinese (simplified): 优质设计师服装，采用精细的材料和编织，通常由银河系的富人和权贵穿着，但在重要场合，平民的衣橱中也不少见。

English: A luxury among the elite, these articles of jewellery would fetch a suitable price on the market as long as there's someone out there willing to buy such pieces.
Chinese (simplified): 精英阶层的奢侈品，这些珠宝首饰只要市场上有人愿意购买，就能卖个好价钱。

English:
[c][FF5555]Restores 150 health.[-][/c]
A hospital-grade Medkit intended to treat traumatic injuries and infections in the field.

[c][00FF00]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][FF5555]恢复150生命值。[-][/c]
一种医用级别的医疗包，旨在治疗战场上的创伤性伤害和感染。

[c][00FF00]使用左键点击工具栏或使用Shift+右键点击库存[-][/c]

English: A specialized hospital-grade Medkit with a 3-part injection process that purges toxins and impurities from the bloodstream and internal organs.\n\n[c][00FF00]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种专业的医用级医疗包，具有三步注射过程，可以清除血液中的毒素和内脏中的杂质。\n\n[c][00FF00]使用左键点击工具栏或使用Shift+右键点击库存[-][/c]

English: A state-of-the-art Medkit used predominantly in industrial applications with a high chance of irradiation. This kit uses formulated nano-particles to purge radiation and dead cells from the bloodstream and soft tissues.\n\n[c][00FF00]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种在工业应用中广泛使用的最先进的医疗包，这些应用中存在高辐射风险。该医疗包含有配方化的纳米粒子，用于从血液和软组织中清除辐射和死亡细胞。\n\n[c][00FF00]使用左键点击工具栏或使用Shift+右键点击库存[-][/c]

English:
[c][FF5555]Restores 250 health.[-][/c]
A common item in any Field Medic's kit, this medicated plasma injector rapidly seals wounds, replenishes red blood cells and accelerates natural healing.

[c][00FF00]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][FF5555]恢复250生命值。[-][/c]
这是任何战地医护兵工具箱中的常见物品，这种药用等离子体注射器能够迅速封闭伤口，补充红细胞，并加速自然愈合过程。

[c][00FF00]使用左键点击工具栏或使用Shift+右键点击库存[-][/c]

English:
[c][FF5555]Restores 400 health.[-][/c]
The latest in medical treatment in the field. This Medkit can do everything a standard Health Pack can do, not just better, but faster too.

[c][00FF00]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][FF5555]恢复400生命值。[-][/c]
这是战场上的最新医疗治疗方法。这个医疗包不仅能做标准急救包能做的一切，而且做得更好，速度也更快。

[c][00FF00]使用左键点击工具栏或使用Shift+右键点击库存[-][/c]

English:
[c][FF5555]Treats Fractured Bones[-][/c]
A 3D-printed medical cast that will straighten and hold a limb in place while it heals.
[c][00FF00]Fracture's progress bar will turn GREEN when treated, taking only minutes to fully recover.

[c][FFFFFF]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][FF5555]治疗骨折[-][/c]
一种3D打印的医用石膏，能在愈合过程中固定肢体并使其保持在正确的位置。
[c][00FF00]治疗后，骨折的进度条将变为绿色，仅需几分钟即可完全恢复。[-][/c]

[c][FFFFFF]使用左键点击工具栏或使用Shift+右键点击库存[-][/c]

English: A mass-produced automatic rifle made by InterWeap. Reliable and effective in any kind of terrain it's the mainstay of security forces across the galaxy on both sides of the law.
Chinese (simplified): 由InterWeap制造的大规模生产自动步枪。它在任何地形中都可靠有效，是银河系各地安全力量的主力装备，无论是法律的哪一方。

English: A mass-produced shotgun originally designed for close-quarters defense against pirate boarders. It has since been adopted by both traders and pirates due to it's effectiveness.
Chinese (simplified): 最初为近距离防御海盗登船而设计的大规模生产霰弹枪。由于其有效性，它已经被商人和海盗所采纳。

English: A mass-produced blaster rifle from Arriake Technology. Slightly different from a standard laser rifle, the AAF-07 fires plasma gel pellets using a standard laser charge. A slower-moving projectile with a more forceful impact.
Chinese (simplified): Arriake Technology生产的大规模生产爆破步枪。与标准激光步枪略有不同，AAF-07使用标准激光电池发射等离子凝胶弹丸。它的弹丸飞行速度较慢，但冲击力更强。

English: A hard shell from some kind of large insect. It likely has some medicinal properties or can be used as a binder in some organic products.
Chinese (simplified): 某种大型昆虫的硬壳。它可能具有一些药用特性，或者可以作为某些有机产品的粘合剂。

English: It's a bone. The support structure of vertebrates to which muscle attaches in order to facilitate movement.\nIt has some industrial and medical uses.
Chinese (simplified): 这是一块骨头。是脊椎动物的支撑结构，肌肉附着在上面以促进运动。\n它在工业和医疗方面有一些用途。

English: A qualified power room technician, capable of fine-tuning energy production and efficiency. Freeing up valuable processing power and improving energy efficiency.\n[c][00FFFF]Power Consumption:[-][/c] [c][FFFFFF]-75W[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一名合格的动力室技术员，能够微调能源生产和效率。释放宝贵的处理能力并提高能源效率。\n[c][00FFFF]功耗:[-][/c][c][FFFFFF]-75W[-][/c]

English: A qualified engineer trained to modulate shield energy levels better than a basic AI controller. Freeing up valuable processing power and improving shield efficiency.\n[c][FF00FF]Shield Capacity:[-][/c] [c][FFFFFF]+1000[-][/c]\n[c][FF00FF]Shield Charge:[-][/c] [c][FFFFFF]+50[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一名合格的工程师，被训练来比基本人工智能控制器更好地调制护盾能量水平。释放宝贵的处理能力并提高护盾效率。\n[c][FF00FF]护盾容量:[-][/c][c][FFFFFF]+1000[-][/c]\n[c][FF00FF]护盾充电:[-][/c][c][FFFFFF]+50[-][/c]

English: A seasoned fuel system engineer from the Trade Federation. Can handle promethium feed lines and pressure in the fuel delivery system, freeing up diagnostic processing power and improving fuel distribution.\n[c][00FFFF]Fuel Capacity:[-][/c] [c][FFFFFF]+4000L[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 来自贸易联盟的经验丰富的燃料系统工程师。能够处理钷的供料线和燃油输送系统中的压力，释放诊断处理能力，并提高燃油分配效率。\n[c][00FFFF]燃油容量:[-][/c][c][FFFFFF]+4000L[-][/c]

English: A trained helmsman with years of experience flying everything from freighters to warships. By taking over the system's inertia control systems manually, he can reduce the processing load on the core while improving handling.\n[c][00FF00]Ship Torque:[-][/c] [c][FFFFFF]+5mN[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一名经过训练的舵手，拥有多年从货船到战舰等各种类型飞行器的飞行经验。通过手动接管系统的惯性控制系统，他可以在改善操控性的同时减少核心的处理负载。\n[c][00FF00]扭矩:[-][/c][c][FFFFFF]+5mN[-][/c]

English: A qualified communications officer in charge of ship-to-ship communications and logistics. By manually operating the matter transmitters, he can increase the range of the Logistics Connection outside the ship.\n[c][00FFFF]Logistics Range:[-][/c] [c][FFFFFF]125m[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一名合格的通信官，负责船对船的通信和后勤工作。通过手动操作物质传输器，他可以增加船外后勤连接的范围。\n[c][00FFFF]后勤范围:[-][/c][c][FFFFFF]125米[-][/c]

English: An ensign trained in ship operation and tactics that can assist in any technical aspect as part of the bridge crew, from fire control to radar analysis. Improves CPU management across the board, but lacks any specific abilities.\n[c][00FF00]CPU Capacity:[-][/c] [c][FFFFFF]+3750[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一名在飞船操作和战术方面受过训练的海军少尉，能够作为舰桥团队的一部分，在任何技术方面提供协助，从火力控制到雷达分析。他提高了全面的CPU管理能力，但缺乏任何特定能力。\n[c][00FF00]CPU容量:[-][/c][c][FFFFFF]+3750[-][/c]

English: A security officer with a history of naval service as a weapon specialist. Can order and arrange munitions in a more practical order allowing more ammunition to be crammed into the weapon system without the interference of the onboard logistics system.\n[c][FF6600]Ammunition Capacity:[-][/c] [c][FFFFFF]+4000L[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一名拥有海军武器专家背景的安全官。他可以对弹药进行更有条理的命令和安排，使得在不干扰船上后勤系统的情况下，能够将更多的弹药塞进武器系统。\n[c][FF6600]弹药容量:[-][/c][c][FFFFFF]+4000L[-][/c]

English: A medical officer from the Trade Federation with years of active service on record. Can treat anything from dermal burns to space herpes... probably.\n[c][FF5555]Cures almost every status effect[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 来自贸易联盟的一名医疗官，有多年的活跃服役记录。可以治疗从皮肤烧伤到太空疱疹的各种疾病……可能吧。\n[c][FF5555]几乎治愈所有状态效果[-][/c]

English: A fresh salad composed of Ziraxian red cabbage, Omicronian Daikon, and topped with grilled Ignidon meat.\n[c][B2FF80]Slowly recovers health and increases maximum health. Not very filling though.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一份新鲜的沙拉，主料为兹瑞克斯红卷心菜和奥米克戎萝卜，佐以喷火牛肉\n[c][B2FF80]缓慢回复生命并提升生命上限[-][/c]

English: Ice cold chocolate chip Ice cream. Eat it before it melts!\n[c][008FFF]Protects against high temperatures\nRecovers stamina and rapidly reduces body temperature[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 冰冷的巧克力碎片冰淇淋。在它融化之前吃掉它！\n[c][008FFF]恢复体力和迅速降低体温。\n在炎热的星球上食用效果更佳！[-][/c]

English: A special cocktail made at only a number of bars and restaurants. It burns going down and has an odd spicy aftertaste.\n[c][FF0000]Protects against cold temperatures\nImproves Health and Stamina regeneration[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种只有在少数酒吧和餐馆才能制作的特制鸡尾酒。喝下去时感觉灼热，还有一种奇怪的辛辣余味。\n[c][FF0000]抵御寒冷温度\n提高健康和耐力恢复[-][/c]

English: A special cocktail made at only a number of bars and restaurants. It's smooth with citrus overtones and a grassy smell\n[c][00FFAA]Adds constant regeneration, but is slightly radioactive.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种特殊的鸡尾酒，只在少数酒吧和餐厅里面才有，入口顺滑，带有柑橘的味道和青草的香气\n[c][00FFAA]赋予完全的环境抗性和少量生命再生，不过有一点点辐射[-][/c]

English: A pink milkshake that appears to be very similar to Strawberry with some hint of other mixed berries.\n[c][FF6666]Increases maximum Stamina and increases movement speed by 75%[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种粉红色的奶昔，看起来与草莓非常相似，还带有一些其他混合浆果的暗示。\n[c][FF6666]增加最大体力，并增加75%的移动速度[-][/c]

English: A special cocktail made at only a number of bars and restaurants. It has a sharp, sour taste with a smell like gasoline.[c][008FFF]Massively increases maximum Health, but reduces maximum stamina and movement speed[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种只有在少数酒吧和餐馆才能制作的特制鸡尾酒。它味道尖锐、酸涩，闻起来像汽油。\n[c][008FFF]大幅增加最大生命值，但减少最大体力和移动速度[-][/c]
[c][008FFF]恢复体力和快速降低体温。在炎热的星球上效果不错！[-][/c]
[c][B2FF80]缓慢恢复生命值，并增加最大生命值和耐力[-][/c]

English: [c][FF0000]Protected against cold temperatures!\nHealth and Stamina recovery improved![-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): [c][FF0000]抵御寒冷温度！\n健康和耐力恢复提高！[-][/c]

English: What the hell did I just drink?\n[c][00FF80]Gained the regenerative abilities of The Legacy. Also gained their radioactivity...[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 我刚才到底喝了什么？\n[c][00FF80]获得了遗留者的再生能力。同时也获得了它们的放射性...[-][/c]

English: Strawberry, Yum!\n[c][FF6666]Maximum Stamina and Movement Speed increased![-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 草莓，真好吃！\n[c][FF6666]最大耐力和移动速度提升！[-][/c]

English: I feel really weird right now...\n[c][008FFF]Maximum Health Increased by 400!\nMaximum Stamina and Speed Reduced by 50%[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 我现在感觉真的很奇怪...\n[c][008FFF]最大生命值增加400！\n最大耐力和速度减少50%[-][/c]

English: A System Core module infected with legacy quantum technology that provides superior processing power.
Chinese (simplified): 一种被遗留者量子技术感染的系统核心模块，提供卓越的处理能力。

English: An auto-loading container that utilizes the logistics system to load ammunition automatically into turrets and weapons.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]Required in order to load any weapon on the same structure[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一个自动装填容器，利用物流系统自动将弹药装入炮台和武器中。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]需要用它来为同一结构上的任何武器装载弹药[-][/c]

English: Drilling mode for use on planets for the extraction of resources from the ground and surface rocks.
Chinese (simplified): 用于行星上的采矿钻井，从地面和地表岩石中提取资源。

English: Drilling mode for use in space against asteroids in zero gravity.
Chinese (simplified): 在太空中用于小行星的采矿钻井，适用于零重力环境。

English: Device used for modifying and customizing weapons with damage, recoil, accuracy and reload speed upgrades.
Chinese (simplified): 用于升级武器的伤害、后坐力、准确性和装填速度的设备。

English: Anti-Collision weapon for Patrol Vessels to be placed on their nose to prevent players from face-hugging or ramming the ship to stop it.\nWill destroy the front of the player's ship on close contact.
Chinese (simplified): 巡逻舰的防碰撞武器，放置在舰船的前端，以防止玩家紧贴或撞击舰船以使其停止。\n在近距离接触时，会摧毁玩家舰船的前部。

English: An after-market suit attachment that fills the space between suit layers with a non-Newtonian fluid that hardens when struck, providing additional armor from impacts and damage.\n[c][FFBB00]Can only be attached to a suit using an Armor Locker[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种售后市场服装附件，通过在服装层之间填充一种非牛顿流体来填补空间，这种流体在受到撞击时会变硬，提供额外的防护装甲以抵御冲击和伤害。\n[c][FFBB00]只能使用装甲储物柜附加到服装上[-][/c]

English: An after-market suit attachment that applies a nanogel to the lining of the suit, providing better insulation against environmental sources and amplifying nerve connectivity between the suit and it's wearer.\n[c][FFBB00]Can only be attached to a suit using an Armor Locker[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种售后市场服装附件，将纳米凝胶应用于服装内衬，提供更好的绝缘效果以抵御环境因素，并增强服装与穿着者之间的神经连接性。\n[c][FFBB00]只能使用装甲储物柜附加到服装上[-][/c]

English: An after-market suit attachment that uses a neurokinetic weave to amplify force feedback and dampen inertia during physical movement.\n[c][FFBB00]Can only be attached to a suit using an Armor Locker[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种售后市场服装附件，使用神经运动编织技术来增强力反馈，并在身体运动期间减少惯性。\n[c][FFBB00]只能使用装甲储物柜附加到服装上[-][/c]

English: An after-market suit attachment comprised of a secondary high-pressure oxygen tank and regulator.\n[c][FFBB00]Can only be attached to a suit using an Armor Locker[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种售后市场服装附件，包括一个次级高压氧气罐和调节器。\n[c][FFBB00]只能使用装甲储物柜附加到服装上[-][/c]

English: An after-market suit attachment that adds an improved plasma injector to the jetpack for more efficient thrust vectoring.\n[c][FFBB00]Can only be attached to a suit using an Armor Locker[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种售后市场服装附件，为喷气背包增加了改进的等离子体喷射器，以实现更高效的推力矢量控制。\n[c][FFBB00]只能使用装甲储物柜附加到服装上[-][/c]

English: An after-market suit attachment that utilizes a thermoconductive nanogel added between layers of the suit that improves resistance to cold and stabilizes suit structure in the vacuum of space.\n[c][FFBB00]Can only be attached to a suit using an Armor Locker[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种售后市场服装附件，利用热导纳米凝胶填充在服装层之间，提高了对寒冷的抵抗力，并在太空真空中稳定了服装结构。\n[c][FFBB00]只能使用装甲储物柜附加到服装上[-][/c]

English: An after-market suit attachment that consists of external thermocouples to shunt excess temperature from the suit into advanced heat sinks, keeping the wearer cool in the most extreme of environments.\n[c][FFBB00]Can only be attached to a suit using an Armor Locker[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种售后市场服装附件，由外部热电偶组成，将服装中多余的温度转移到先进的散热器中，使穿着者在最极端的环境中保持凉爽。\n[c][FFBB00]只能使用装甲储物柜附加到服装上[-][/c]

English: An after-market suit attachment that infuses the suit's lining with a sathium-based ferrofluid that provides additional protection from gamma radiation without affecting mobility.\n[c][FFBB00]Can only be attached to a suit using an Armor Locker[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种售后市场服装附件，将基于钑的磁性流体注入服装衬里，提供额外的伽马辐射防护，且不影响机动性。\n[c][FFBB00]只能使用装甲储物柜附加到服装上[-][/c]

English: An after-market suit attachment comprised of reinforced servos and carrying harness to maximize carry capacity. A popular choice in the industrial sector for transporting heavy goods.\n[c][FFBB00]Can only be attached to a suit using an Armor Locker[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种售后市场服装附件，由加强的伺服机构和携带背带组成，以最大化携带能力。在工业领域运输重物的流行选择。\n[c][FFBB00]只能使用装甲储物柜附加到服装上[-][/c]

English: Unpurified water in a transparent and permiable fluid container. Can be stored, frozen or poured into an appropriate space like an ordinary block.\n[c][00BBFF]The water will not flow beyond it's border and has the full fluid mass of it's dimensions (7250L).[-][/c]\n[c][FFBB00]Cannot be used as a water source for extractors.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 未净化的水在一个透明且可渗透的流体容器中。可以存储、冷冻或倒入适当的空间，如普通方块。\n[c][00BBFF]水不会流出其边界，并具有其尺寸的全部流体质量(7250升)。[-][/c]\n[c][FFBB00]不能用作提取器的水源。[-][/c]

English: A commercial constructor manufactured by Polaris for use by colonists, private industrial outposts, the Trade Federation and even the Zirax Empire.\nThese constructors were standard use across settled space until UCH models became available on the galactic market, that while more CPU-intensive were less energy-intensive.
Chinese (simplified): 由波拉利斯制造的商业建造机，供殖民者、私人工业前哨站、贸易联盟甚至兹瑞克斯帝国使用。\n这些建造机在定居空间中是标准用途，直到UCH型号在银河市场上可用，尽管这些型号对CPU要求更高，但能耗更低。

English: Manufactured by Polaris for the last 80 years, these Deconstructors were standard among salvagers until less energy-intensive UCH models became available on the galactic market. Which one is better is a hotly debated topic in many forums.
Chinese (simplified): 由波拉利斯生产了80年的这些解构机，在银河市场上能耗更低的UCH型号出现之前，一直是回收者中的标准设备。哪一种更好是许多论坛上热议的话题。

English: Made from processing grain and fruit into biofuel, Bioethanol can be converted into an emergency fuel source in many plasma generators with greater efficiency than Biodiesel.\nIt's recommended that you clean your generators and fuel tanks after use however.
Chinese (simplified): 由谷物和水果加工成的生物乙醇，可以在许多等离子发电机中转化为紧急燃料来源，其效率比生物柴油更高。\n不过，建议使用后清洁您的发电机和油箱。

English:
Storage Bay for Planetary Drones that functions as an Ammunition Controller for Drone Launchpads.

Power on the Drone Bay and Drone Launchpad to launch drones on a planet.
Power off the devices to command the drones to return to the launchpad and return to storage.

Will function in space, but be too slow for practical use.
Chinese (simplified):
用于存放行星无人机的存储舱，同时作为无人机发射台的弹药控制器使用。

启动无人机舱和无人机发射台的电源，以在行星上发射无人机。
关闭这些设备，以命令无人机返回发射台并返回存储舱。

该功能在太空中也可使用，但速度过慢，不太实用。

English:
Storage Bay for Orbital Drones that functions as an Ammunition Controller for Drone Launchpads.

Power on the Drone Bay and Drone Launchpad to launch drones in space.
Power off the devices to command the drones to return to the launchpad and return to storage.

Will function on planets, but the drones have no object avoidance on planets and will crash into the ground.
Chinese (simplified):
轨道无人机的存储舱，充当无人机发射台的弹药控制器。

启动无人机舱和无人机发射台，以在太空中发射无人机。
关闭这些设备，以命令无人机返回发射台并返回存储舱。
将在行星上工作，但无人机在行星上没有物体避让功能，会撞向地面。

English: Combat Drone equipped with a 30mm Autocannon designed for short-ranged operation on planets.\nMust be placed inside a Drone Bay with a functional Drone Launchpad.\nWill return to base when the launchpad is turned off.
Chinese (simplified): 装备有30毫米自动炮的战斗无人机，设计用于行星上的短程作战。\n必须放置在带有功能正常的无人机发射台的无人机舱内。\n当发射台关闭时，将返回基地。

English: High-speed Interceptor Drone equipped with a burst plasma cannon designed for short-ranged operation in space.\nMust be placed inside a Drone Bay with a functional Drone Launchpad.\nWill return to base when the launchpad is turned off.
Chinese (simplified): 高速拦截无人机，装备有爆发等离子炮，设计用于太空中的短程作战。\n必须放置在带有功能正常的无人机发射台的无人机舱内。\n当发射台关闭时，将返回基地。

English: A drone Launchpad that is required to launch drones stored in a Drone Bay and give them a place to return to when powered off.
Chinese (simplified): 一个无人机发射台，它是用来从无人机舱中发射无人机，并在无人机关闭电源时提供一个返回的地方。

English: A lightweight steel blade with a polymer handle. Although rarely needed in combat, it's a reliable piece of kit in survival situations.\n[c][37D2FF]Consumes stamina to attack[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一把轻质钢制刀片，带有聚合物手柄。虽然在战斗中很少需要使用，但在生存情况下它是可靠的装备。\n[c][37D2FF]攻击时消耗体力[-][/c]

English: EnTech's model-7 Plasma cutter.\nTypically a more utilitarian design for cutting away debris and wreckage. It became common to customize the frame into an antiquated sword design.
Chinese (simplified): EnTech公司 7号等离子切割器。\n通常是一种更加实用的设计，用于切割碎片和残骸。人们习惯于将框架定制成过时的剑形设计。

English: Reinforced heavy doors designed to contain explosions and fire from spreading to other parts of a structure.\n[c][37D2FF]High Blast Resistance[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 增强型重型门，设计用于防止爆炸和火灾蔓延到建筑的其他部分。\n[c][37D2FF]高爆破抗性[-][/c]

English: A compact, multi-platform Gravity Generator developed by Polaris. Usable on any platform, they are rapidly replacing standard units despite their significantly higher costs.
Chinese (simplified): 由波拉利斯开发的紧凑型、多平台重力发生器。它们可以在任何平台上使用，尽管成本显著更高，但正在迅速取代标准单元。

English: A massive satellite dish for long-ranged communication.\nUnfortunately, this technology is outdated and provides no functionality compared to your modern equipment, making it wholly decorative.
Chinese (simplified): 一个用于远程通信的大型卫星天线。\n不幸的是，这项技术已经过时，与您的现代设备相比没有任何功能，使其完全成为装饰性物品。

English: An oversized antiquated rocket engine that still operates on chemical propellant.\nThis model of thruster hasn't been used in over a century as smaller Ion thrusters replaced the technology.\nNonetheless, it can be retrofitted to function as a normal thruster if you can ignore the ridiculous thruster size...
Chinese (simplified): 一个过大且过时的火箭引擎，仍然使用化学推进剂运作。\n这种型号的推进器已经超过一个世纪没有使用了，因为更小的离子推进器取代了这项技术。\n尽管如此，如果你可以忽略那荒谬的推进器尺寸，它仍然可以被改造成正常运作的推进器...

English: A Shuttle Engine once used on both military and commercial spacecrafts that has since been long outdated by modern developments in Ion Thruster technology.\nAlthough impractical, this model has been retrofitted to function as a regular Ion Thruster, albeit a very large one.
Chinese (simplified): 一种曾经用于军事和商业航天器的穿梭机引擎，但随着现代离子推进器技术的发展，它早已过时。\n尽管不实用，但这种型号已经被改造，可以作为常规离子推进器使用，尽管体积相当庞大。

English:
[c][FF0000]Debug Multitool for creative mode use ONLY[-][/c]
Indestructible
Unlimited Ammunition
Instant Salvage
Fine-Damage Modes
Chinese (simplified):
[c][FF0000]仅限创意模式使用的调试多功能工具[-][/c]
不可摧毁
无限弹药
即时拆解
精细损伤模式

English: [c][FF0000]Access Denied[-][/c]\nUse '{0}' to enter a valid access code
Chinese (simplified): [c][FF0000]访问被拒绝[-][/c]\n使用'{0}'输入有效的访问代码

English: [c][FF0000]Foreign Core Detected[-][/c]\nCore must be removed or replaced to proceed.
Chinese (simplified): [c][FF0000]检测到外来核心[-][/c]\n必须移除或替换核心才能继续。

English: [c][FF0000]Blueprint Complexity exceeds the limits of the server[-][/c]\nWill negatively affect local and server performance if used.
Chinese (simplified): [c][FF0000]蓝图复杂度超出了服务器的限制[-][/c]\n如果使用，将对本地和服务器性能产生负面影响。

English: Cargo Container with dialog function for POI use.
Chinese (simplified): 带有对话框功能的货物集装箱，用于POI。

English: Non-functional automining device that can be placed as a decorative object.\nAccepts dialog options for POI construction.\n[c][FF0000]Avoid overuse due to performance issues[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种非功能性的自动采矿装置，可以作为装饰性物品放置。\n接受对话框选项用于POI的建设。\n[c][FF0000]由于性能问题，请避免过度使用[-][/c]
改进型离子喷射推进器(SV)

English: A block group for placing decorative blocks. See tooltips on individual blocks.\n\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一组可放置的装饰用方块. 参见每个方块单独的说明.\n\n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园..[/i][-][/c]

English:
A warning light with a built in alarm. Can be controlled via signals.
Damage with a T1 Multitool to change the color of the light between red, orange, and yellow based on how damaged the light is. Note: repairing your ship will reset the light color to red.

[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
内建警报的告警灯光，可以通过电路信号控制.
使用T1多功能枪对其造成伤害会使其根据所受伤害程度由红变橙再变黄. 注意:维修飞船会将颜色重置为红色.

[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English:
A warning light. Can be controlled via signals.
Damage with a T1 Multitool to change the color of the light between red, orange, and yellow based on how damaged the light is. Note: repairing your ship will reset the light color to red.

[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
告警灯光，可以通过电路信号控制.
使用T1多功能枪对其造成伤害会使其根据所受伤害程度由红变橙再变黄. 注意:维修飞船会将颜色重置为红色.

[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]

English: A panel that can act as a switch to control signals.\n\n[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一个可以作为开关来控制信号的面板.\n\n[c][A9A9A9][i]需要伊甸园计划或重铸伊甸园.[/i][-][/c]
嵌入式墙面控制台(蓝色细型)
一种装饰性的全息显示屏。
嵌入式墙面控制台(蓝色1x1型)
嵌入式墙面控制台(橙色小型)

English:
Uses a combination of holograms and magnetically suspended nanoparticles to create a three dimensional projection of a variety of visual effects.
Effect style can be changed in the RMB menu while placing and turned on or off in the control panel or via signals.

[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
使用全息图和磁悬浮纳米粒子的组合来创建各种视觉效果的三维投影.
效果风格可以通过鼠标右键改变，并在控制面板或通过信号打开或关闭.

[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]

English: Reflects holographic projections off magnetized nanoparticles to give the illusion of a flame.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 从磁化纳米粒子反射全息投影，产生火焰一般的幻象.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (火焰 对角线)
特效投影仪 (火焰 尾迹)

English: Reflects holographic projections off magnetized nanoparticles to give the illusion of a flame. The visual effect will trail behind your ship while in movement.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 从磁化纳米粒子反射全息投影，产生火焰一般幻象。该视觉效果会在移动时跟随在飞船后面产生拖尾.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (火焰 尾迹 拐角)
特效投影仪 (火焰 蓝色)
特效投影仪 (油 闪光)
特效投影仪 (油 闪光 对角线)
特效投影仪 (钷 闪光)

English: Uses a thick cloud of light absorbing nanoparticles suspended in a magnetic field to give the illusion of smoke.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 使用悬浮在磁场中的浓厚光吸收纳米粒子云来产生烟雾的幻象。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (黑烟 对角线)
特效投影仪 (黑烟 尾迹)

English: Uses a thick cloud of light absorbing nanoparticles suspended in a magnetic field to give the illusion of smoke. The visual effect will trail behind your ship while in movement.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 使用悬浮在磁场中的浓厚光吸收纳米粒子云来产生烟雾的幻象。该视觉效果会在移动时跟随在飞船后面产生拖尾。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (黑烟 尾迹 拐角)
特效投影仪 (灰烟 对角线)
特效投影仪 (灰烟 尾迹))

English: Uses a thick cloud of light absorbing nanoparticles suspended in a magnetic field to give the illusion of smoke. The visual effect will trail behind your ship while in movement.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 使用悬浮在磁场中的浓厚光吸收纳米粒子云来产生烟雾的幻象。该视觉效果会在移动时跟随在飞船后面产生拖尾。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]

English: Uses a thin cloud of light absorbing nanoparticles suspended in a magnetic field to give the illusion of steam.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 使用悬浮在磁场中的稀薄光吸收纳米粒子云来产生蒸汽的幻象。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (蒸汽 对角线)
特效投影仪 (蓝色引擎尾迹)

English: Leaves behind a thin stream of nanoparticles to give the illusion of an engine trail.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 在后方留下一道细小的纳米粒子流，给人一种发动机尾迹的错觉。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (红色引擎尾迹)

English: Creates an ionized channel that conducts electricity through it.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 创造一条电力可以流通的电离管路。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]

English: Reflects holographic projections off clumps of nanoparticles to give the illusion of fireflies.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 利用纳米颗粒团块反射全息投影，产生萤火虫的幻象。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (指引环 蓝色)

English:
Arranges nanoparticles into distinct groups and reflects a strong holograpic projection off of them to create a large ring of lights to act as a docking guide for space stations. The ring is several hundred meters in diameter.
Place in the center of your space station.

[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
将纳米颗粒排列成多个不同的分组，并反射出高亮度的全息投影，从而形成一个大的光环，作为空间站的对接指引. 环有数百米大.
置于空间站中心.

[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
特效投影仪 (指引 蓝色)

English: Arranges nanoparticles into distinct groups and reflects a strong holograpic projection off of them to create a line of static docking guides outward from the emitter.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 将纳米颗粒排列成多个不同的分组，并反射出高亮度的全息投影，从而形成由发射器向外的一排静态对接引导线。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
效果投影仪 (指引 橙色)
效果投影仪 (指引 青色 动画)

English:
Arranges nanoparticles into distinct groups and reflects a rotating holograpic projection off of them to project a line of animated docking guides outward from the emitter.
These projections are offset slightly to match up seamlessly when placed next to a static docking guide.

[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
将纳米颗粒排列成多个不同的分组，并反射它们的旋转全息投影，从而由发射器向外投射一条可动对接引导线.
当放置在静态对接导轨旁边时，这些投影会稍微偏移以保证无缝.

[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座会在开启30秒后自动隐藏自身，关闭投影仪以揭示底座本身.[-][/c]
效果投影仪(引导黄色动画)
效果投影仪(白色圆锥形对角)

English: Arranges nanoparticles into distinct groups and reflects a rotating holograpic projection off of them to project the illusion of a cone of light.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 将纳米粒子排列成不同的组，并通过它们反射旋转的全息投影，以投射出光锥的幻觉。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座在开启30秒后自动隐藏。关闭效果投影仪以显示发射器底座。[-][/c]
效果投影仪(蓝色圆锥形对角)
效果投影仪(橙色圆锥形对角)

English: Reflects holographic projections off magnetized nanoparticles to give the illusion of sparks.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 通过磁化的纳米粒子反射全息投影，给人以火花的幻觉。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座在开启30秒后自动隐藏。关闭效果投影仪以显示发射器底座。[-][/c]
效果投影仪(全息赛博格)

English: Bounces light off a matrix of nanoparticles to generate a holographic projection.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn effect projector off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 利用纳米粒子矩阵反射光线以生成全息投影。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座在开启30秒后会自动隐藏。关闭效果投影仪以显示发射器底座。[-][/c]
效果投影仪(大型全息赛博格)

English: A decorative holographic emitter that displays a random corporate advertisement. The emitter periodically cycles through different displays.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 20 seconds. Turn holographic emitter off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种装饰性全息发射器，显示随机的企业广告。发射器会定期循环不同的显示内容。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座在开启20秒后自动隐藏。关闭全息发射器以显示发射器底座。[-][/c]

English: A decorative holographic emitter tied in to the Trade Federation Global Market Tracking System.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 20 seconds. Turn holographic emitter off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种装饰性全息发射器，连接到贸易联盟全球市场追踪系统。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座在开启20秒后自动隐藏。关闭全息发射器以显示发射器底座。[-][/c]

English: A decorative holographic emitter tuned to the Colonist News Network.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 20 seconds. Turn holographic emitter off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种装饰性全息发射器，调谐至殖民者新闻网络。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座在开启20秒后自动隐藏。关闭全息发射器以显示发射器底座。[-][/c]

English: A decorative holographic emitter that displays random pirate propaganda. The emitter periodically cycles through different displays.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 20 seconds. Turn holographic emitter off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种装饰性全息发射器，显示随机的海盗宣传。发射器会定期循环不同的显示内容。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座在开启20秒后自动隐藏。关闭全息发射器以显示发射器底座。[-][/c]

English: A decorative holographic emitter that shows random wanted posters. The emitter periodically cycles through different displays.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 20 seconds. Turn holographic emitter off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种装饰性全息发射器，展示随机的通缉海报。发射器会定期循环不同的显示内容。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座在开启20秒后自动隐藏。关闭全息发射器以显示发射器底座。[-][/c]

English: A decorative holo poster that cycles through random images.
Chinese (simplified): 一种装饰性全息海报，循环显示随机图像。

English: Repair Charges are used to repair damaged and deformed blocks using a Repair Bay instead of consuming raw resources.\n[c][00FFFF]Can only be used by a Repair Bay[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 维修电池用于在修复舱中修复损坏和变形的方块，而不是消耗原始资源。\n[c][00FFFF]只能在修复舱中使用[-][/c]

English: The latest Assault Rifle developed by the UCH using techniques and materials found in the Andromeda galaxy. It exhibits far better performance than older models of assault rifle.
Chinese (simplified): UCH利用在仙女座星系中发现的技术和材料开发的最新突击步枪。它的表现远远优于旧型号的突击步枪。

English: A modern Combat shotgun developed by the UCH using hybridized engineering of both Polaris and the Zirax Empire to improve the older model UC shotgun.
Chinese (simplified): UCH利用波拉利斯和兹瑞克斯帝国的混合工程技术开发的现代战斗霰弹枪，以改进旧型号的UC霰弹枪。

English:
A weapon system wholly unique to The Legacy that uses a programmable antimatter stream to annihilate atomic bonds, even through shields.
[c][00FF00]High damage vs Metal Hull Blocks
50% Shield Penetration[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]-33% Damage to Xenosteel
Not usable by players[-][/c]
[c][FF00FF]60,000 Shield Damage per minute[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种完全独特的武器系统，属于遗留者(The Legacy)，它使用可编程的反物质流来湮灭原子键，甚至可以穿透护盾。

[c][00FF00]对装甲块造成高伤害
50% 护盾穿透[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]-33% 对异星钢的伤害[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]玩家无法使用[-][/c]
[c][FF00FF]每分钟60,000护盾伤害[-][/c]

English:
Developed by the Brotherhood of Farr, the Ion Beam Turret is locally known as "The Golden Law" and is based on Legacy Disruptor technology. While it lacks destructive capabilities, it is highly effective at stripping the electrons from shields.
[c][00FF00]High Shield Damage[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]No Hull Damage
Cannot be retrieved once placed[-][/c]
[c][FF00FF]60,000 Shield Damage per minute[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
由法尔兄弟会(Brotherhood of Farr)开发的离子光束炮塔在当地被称为“黄金法则”(The Golden Law)，它基于遗留者(Legacy)的破坏者技术。虽然它没有破坏性能力，但在剥离护盾的电子方面非常有效。

[c][00FF00]高护盾伤害[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]无船体伤害
一旦放置，无法取回[-][/c]
[c][FF00FF]每分钟60,000护盾伤害[-][/c]

English:
An oversized Ion Cell Battery used to power the Brotherhood of Farr's Ion Beam Technology.
[c][00FF00]High Shield Damage
High Mechanoid and Drone Damage[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]No Hull Damage[-][/c]
[c][FF00FF]60,000 Shield Damage per minute[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种超大号的离子电池，用于为法尔兄弟会的离子光束技术提供动力。

[c][00FF00]高护盾伤害
对机械人和无人机造成高伤害[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]无船体伤害[-][/c]
[c][FF00FF]每分钟60,000护盾伤害[-][/c]

English:
Decorative trees for safe and easy transplant around your base which contain a nutrient supply for survival in the harshest of climates.
Will clip through blocks once placed

[c][FF0000]Trees have a hard placement limit for performance[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
用于基地周围安全且易于移植的装饰性树木，它们包含营养供应，能在最恶劣的气候条件下生存。
一旦放置，树木会穿透方块。

[c][FF0000]为了性能考虑，树木的放置有严格的限制[-][/c]

English: A reinforced combat steel Bulldozer Blade traditionally used for landscaping and demolition, can demolish trees, surface rocks and function as a passable shield to incoming fire.\n[c][00FF00]+50% Blast Resistance[-][/c]\n[c][FF0000]Cannot Damage Structures[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种加固的战斗钢推土机刀片，传统上用于景观设计和拆除工作，能够拆除树木、地表岩石，并作为抵御来袭火力的可行护盾。

[c][00FF00]+50% 爆破抗性[-][/c]
[c][FF0000]不能损坏结构[-][/c]

English: Decorative devices with a degree of durability that can be used internally or externally for aesthetics.\n[c][FF0000]Overuse will affect performance[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 具有一定耐久度的装饰性设备，可以内外用于美观。\n[c][FF0000]过度使用会影响性能[-][/c]

English: Decorative turbine that can be used as ventilation covers. Can be turned off and on with signal logic.\nDoes not inflict damage if stepped on... yet.\nEmits sound when turned on.
Chinese (simplified): 可用作通风口盖的装饰性涡轮机。可以通过信号逻辑开关。\n踩上去不会造成伤害... 到目前为止。\n开启时发出声音。

English: Block Group for POIs that damage, explode or otherwise do nasty things when poked, prodded or inhaled.\n\n[c][FF0000]For POI use ONLY[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 用于POI的方块组，当被戳、戳或吸入时会造成伤害、爆炸或做其他坏事。\n\n[c][FF0000]仅限POI使用[-][/c]

English: Laser fences inflict instant death on contact with a player or NPC.\nCannot be turned off.
Chinese (simplified): 激光围栏接触玩家或NPC时会立即致命。\n不能关闭。

English: Toxic Gas inflicts 50 damage per second that a player or NPC is in contact with it.
Chinese (simplified): 有毒气体会在玩家或NPC接触到它时每秒造成50点伤害。

English: Combustible Fuel Drum. Will explode if shot, dealing damage to all surrounding enemies.\nCan be detonated via signal.
Chinese (simplified): 易燃的燃料桶。如果被射击会爆炸，对周围所有敌人造成伤害。\n可以通过信号引爆。
嵌入式墙面控制台(蓝色1x1双倍)
嵌入式墙面控制台(蓝色1x1四倍)

English: A mobile repair pad designed for the repair and maintenance of spacecrafts including both Small Vessels and Capital Vessels. Requires a Repair Console.\n[c][FF0000]Orientation cannot be changed[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种为小型飞船和大型舰船的修理和维护设计的移动修理垫。需要一个修理控制台。\n[c][FF0000]方向不能更改[-][/c]

English: A semi-automatic shotgun that uses magnetized coils to rapidly accelerate projectiles allowing for a greater effective range compared to other shotguns at the expense of damage and ammo capacity.
Chinese (simplified): 一种半自动霰弹枪，使用磁化线圈快速加速弹丸，与其他霰弹枪相比，允许更大的有效射程，但代价是降低伤害和弹药容量。

English: A scoped combat rifle commonly used by mobile infantry for its ability to function proficiently at both long and short ranges.
Chinese (simplified): 一种带瞄准镜的战斗步枪，因其在长距离和短距离上都能高效发挥作用而通常由机动步兵使用。

English: A compact SMG used for short range combat. Favored by criminals and smugglers for its easy concealment and light weight.
Chinese (simplified): 一种紧凑型冲锋枪，用于近战。因其易于隐藏和轻便而受到罪犯和走私者的青睐。

English: A Trade Federation spacesuit that's been the standard for over a century.\nUnsurpassed protection against the vacuum of space, with large O2 tanks and a strong jetpack.\n[c][FF0000]Not rated for use in combat[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种贸易联盟的太空服，一个多世纪以来一直是标准配置。\n在对抗太空真空方面提供无与伦比的保护，配备大型氧气罐和强大的喷气背包。\n[c][FF0000]不适用于战斗评级[-][/c]

English: A Polaris Industrial Suit used for working in hostile environments where protection from high temperatures and radiation is paramount and where heavy objects need moving.\n[c][FF0000]Not recommended for combat or cold conditions[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种波拉利斯工业服，用于在恶劣环境中工作，这些环境需要最大程度的保护以抵御高温和辐射，并且需要移动重物。\n[c][FF0000]不推荐用于战斗或寒冷条件[-][/c]

English: The Titan Suit foregoes and life support function to provide the absolute maximum in off-the-shelf protection, with everything else going into keeping you upright and moving with all that added armor.\n[c][FF0000]No Life Support Functions\nNo Jetpack[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
泰坦战斗装甲放弃了生命支持功能，以提供现成的最大程度的保护，所有其他功能都投入到让你在增加的装甲下保持直立和移动。

[c][FF0000]没有生命支持功能
没有喷气背包[-][/c]

English: Anti-Missile Countermeasure that will deploy flares behind a ship that will block projectiles flying through them and interfere with turret tracking for a few seconds.\n[c][FF0000]Long Reload Time[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 反导弹干扰措施，会在飞船后方部署信号弹，这些信号弹可以阻挡穿过它们的射弹，并在几秒钟内干扰炮塔追踪。\n[c][FF0000]长装填时间[-][/c]

English: Anti-Missile Countermeasure that's deployed behind a ship that will block projectiles flying through them and interfere with turret tracking for a few seconds.
Chinese (simplified): 反导弹干扰措施，部署在飞船后方，能够阻挡穿过它们的射弹，并在几秒钟内干扰炮塔追踪。

English:
[c][00FFAA]Legacy Boss[-][/c]
Devices, Weapons and Cores can be placed inside its body, where they will be invincible until the block is destroyed by weapon fire.
Invincible shield when turned off
Alternating shield over exposed core when turned on
Chinese (simplified):
[c][00FFAA]遗留者首领[-][/c]
设备、武器和核心可以放置在其体内，在方块被武器火力摧毁之前，它们将是无敌的。
关闭时无敌护盾
开启时交替护盾覆盖暴露的核心

English: Console interface that can be used as a switch to send signals when interacted with.
Chinese (simplified): 控制台界面，可以作为开关使用，在互动时发送信号。

English: Multi-functional remote turret capable of mining, repair and salvage into a Harvest Controller.\nMust be controlled manually via the Device Menu\n[c][00FFFF]Can Mine, Repair and Salvage[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 多功能遥控炮塔，能够将采集、修复和回收功能集成到一个收获控制器中。\n必须通过设备菜单手动控制。\n[c][00FFFF]可以进行采矿、修复和回收[-][/c]

English:
[c][FFFF00]This block ID is no longer valid. Please update your blueprints with the new version of this block as soon as possible.[-][/c] 

[c][FF0000]This block will be removed from the scenario and your blueprints in a future update.[-][/c] 
If this is a player block you can pick it up via multitool to obtain the new block version. For POI blocks you will need to manually replace. 
[c][A9A9A9][i]Requires Project Eden or Reforged Eden.[/i][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][FFFF00]此区块ID已失效。请尽快更新您的蓝图以使用此区块的新版本。[-][/c] 

[c][FF0000]在未来的更新中，此区块将被从场景和您的蓝图中移除。[-][/c] 
如果是玩家区块，您可以通过多功能工具将其拾取以获取新的区块版本。对于POI区块，您需要手动替换。

English: [c][FFFF00]THIS ITEM IS DEPRECATED AND WILL BE REMOVED IN A FUTURE UPDATE. PLEASE DELETE THIS ITEM FROM YOUR INVENTORY.\nIF YOU OBTAINED THIS ITEM IN SURVIVAL PLEASE REPORT THE ISSUE TO THE SCENARIO DEVELOPER OR YOUR SERVER ADMIN.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): [c][FFFF00]此物品已弃用，将在未来的更新中移除。请从你的库存中删除此物品。\n如果你在生存模式中获得了此物品，请向场景开发者或你的服务器管理员报告此问题。[-][/c]

English: Effects Volume [c][ffff00](doesn't affect custom sounds! Keep at 100% in RE)[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 效果音效 [c][ffff00](不影响自定义声音！在RE中保持100%)[-][/c]]

English:
[c][ffff00]An internal error occurred while playing [b]Reforged Eden 2[/b].
Do not report this to the game developers via email.[-][/c]

Please see the [b]Reforged Eden 2 Workshop[/b] for support on the scenario or contact your server admin if playing on a multiplayer server.
Deutsch: Ein interner Fehler ist aufgetreten!\nBitte beschreibe in der vorbereiteten Email kurz was passiert ist - danke!
Français: Une erreur interne s'est produite !\nVeuillez insérer une courte description dans l'email préparé - merci !
Italiano: Si è verificato un errore interno!\nInserisci una breve descrizione all'interno della segnalazione, grazie!
Spanish: ¡Se ha producido un error interno!\nPor favor, escribe una pequeña descripción del mismo en este correo - ¡Gracias!
Portuguese (Euro): Ocorreu um erro interno!\nInsira uma breve descrição no email elaborado. Obrigado!
Portuguese (Brazil): Um erro interno ocorreu!\nPor favor insira uma breve descrição no email preparado - Obrigado!
Polish: Wystąpił błąd!\nWprowadź krótki opis w załączonym e-mailu - dziękujemy!
Russian: Произошла внутренняя ошибка!\nПожалуйста, вставьте описание ошибки в подготовленное письмо - спасибо!
Japanese: 内部エラーが発生しました!\n準備された電子メールに簡単な説明を挿入してください - ありがとう!
Chinese (simplified):
[c][ffff00]在玩[b]Reforged Eden 2[/b]时发生了一个内部错误。
不要通过电子邮件向游戏开发者报告这个问题。[-][/c]

请查看[b]Reforged Eden 2 Workshop[/b]以获取关于场景的支持，或者如果您在多人服务器上玩，请与您的服务器管理员联系。

English:
[c][00ffff]>>>Read the PDA First[-][/c] [sup][c][ffff00](F1)[-][/c][/sup][c][00ffff]<<<[-][/c][sup]

[c][00ffff]Missions:[-][/c] Missions are managed under the Solo Missions tab. Start completing the Reforged Galaxy or Project Eden story missions to unlock additional missions.
[c][00ffff]Empyriopedia:[-][/c] Contains a comprehensive encyclopedia of the scenario and can answer many of your questions. Additional entries are unlocked as you progress through the scenario.
[c][00ffff]Journey Book:[-][/c] Shows a log of previous mission dialog.

[c][00ffff]Tooltips:[-][/c] Tooltips provide important information on many items and devices. Mouse over any item in your inventory, constructor, or tech tree to view details.

[c][00ffff]Planets and Sectors:[-][/c] Planets and sectors in the current solar system are scanned and a basic description of each can be viewed on the local or solar system map.

[c][00ffff]Galaxy:[-][/c] Project Eden contains a large galaxy viewable on the galaxy map. Star class and faction territory change what you may find in a star system.

[c][00ffff]Mass, Volume and CPU:[-][/c] The mass, volume, and CPU restrictions are enabled by default. Use the logistics system to move items too large to fit in the player inventory.

[c][00ffff]Escaping your starting system:[-][/c] Resources to build a basic small vessel can be found on your starting planet.
Resources for a warp capable small vessel can be found on the moon of your starting planet.
Resources for a warp capable capital vessel are on other planets in your starting solar system.
Advanced resources are found in other star systems.[/sup]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][00ffff]>>>首先阅读PDA[-][/c] [sup][c][ffff00](F1)[-][/c][/sup][c][00ffff]<<<[-][/c][sup]

[c][00ffff]任务:[-][/c] 任务在单独任务标签下管理。开始完成重制银河系或伊甸园项目故事任务，以解锁额外任务。
[c][00ffff]百科全书:[-][/c] 包含场景的综合百科全书，可以回答许多问题。随着你在场景中的进展，额外的条目会被解锁。
[c][00ffff]旅程书:[-][/c] 显示前一个任务对话的日志。

[c][00ffff]工具提示:[-][/c] 工具提示提供了许多物品和设备的重要信息。将鼠标悬停在你库存、构造器或科技树中的任何物品上，以查看详细信息。

[c][00ffff]星球和区域:[-][/c] 扫描当前太阳系的星球和区域，可以在本地或太阳系地图上查看每个星球的基本描述。

[c][00ffff]星系:[-][/c] 伊甸园项目包含一个可以在星系地图上看到的大型星系。星类和派系领土会改变你在星系中的发现。

[c][00ffff]质量、体积和CPU:[-][/c] 默认情况下，质量、体积和CPU限制是启用的。使用后勤系统移动太大而无法放入玩家库存的物品。

[c][00ffff]逃离你的起始系统:[-][/c] 在你的起始星球上可以找到建造基础小型飞船的资源。在起始星球的月球上可以找到用于翘曲的小型飞船的资源。在起始太阳系的其它星球上可以找到用于翘曲的大型飞船的资源。在其他星系中可以找到高级资源。[/sup]

English: The Drone Swarm is a deadly menace.
Chinese (simplified): 无人机群是一个致命的威胁。

English: Alien drones of unknown origin. Hostile.
Chinese (simplified): 未知来源的外星无人机。敌对的。

English: A geothermal generator usable on planets with high geological activity. Reduces the power usage of your base while active.\nInteract with the geothermal generator after placement to begin the activation process. Requires unlocking Active Geothermal Generator in the tech tree.\n[c][FFFFFF]This is the closest we can add to real geothermal power in a scenario.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种在地质活动频繁的星球上可用的地热发电机。在激活状态下可以减少你的基地的电力消耗。\n放置后与地热发电机互动以开始激活过程。需要在科技树中解锁“活动地热发电机”。\n[c][FFFFFF]这是我们在场景中能添加的最接近真实地热能的东西。[-][/c]

English: Active geothermal generators reduce the power usage of your base.\nRequires activating a geothermal generator using a geological core sample.\nBase will still require a standard generator and fuel tank to run.

English:
For the large scale extraction of resources from water.

[sup][c][FFFFFF]-Must be placed on a base within logistics range of the [b]Lake[/b] (internal name Water) biome.

English:
A fixed mining laser for mining dense and rich ice asteroids found in special sites.

English: An early warning system that provides an audible warning when a threat is detected within range and line of sight in front of the sentry alarm. Recommended to assign to a shortcut on the control panel for easy toggling.

English:
A station used for the launching of probes and scanning for various anomalies.

Accessing this device without an available mission does nothing.

[c][FFFF00]Do not place items into the inventory of this device.[-][/c]

没有可用任务时访问不会有任何效果.

注意: 该物品仍处于测试状态且功能还不正常

English:
A specialized reusable core for claiming a wreck or structure for salvage.
Placing this core will automatically power down the structure to prevent generator overload.
The core can be picked back up intact with [c][FFFF00]F[-] (default hot key) for use on other structures.
[sup][c][ffff00]Placing a core on a POI will permanently disable NPC dialogue on that POI. Do not place cores on mission POIs unless you have completed the mission objectives.[-][/c][/sup]
Chinese (simplified):
一种专用于占据残骸或其他结构以方便拆卸的核心
安装该核心会自动断电以防止过载.
核心可以通过按下 [c][FFFF00]F(默认) [-][/c]来拾起从而用于其他结构.
[sup][c][ffff00]在POI上使用该核心将永久禁用该建筑的NPC对话功能. 因此在你完成任务之前不要把该核心放置于任务POI上.[-][/c][/sup]

English:
[c][ff00ff]Requires Experimental Features to be enabled in the Project Eden Settings menu for this device to be functional.[-][/c]
[sup]An experimental drive that generates a short range wormhole to jump a ship forward a long distance. Usable only in space while piloting a SV or CV.
Once placed, this device should be kept powered OFF as it will be automatically powered ON when needed.
[c][FFFFFF]Instructions for use:
-Place on your ship facing the forward direction and leave the micro jump drive powered OFF.
-Sit in the pilot seat while in space.
-Access the jump drive's interface either by finding it in the control panel of your ship and pressing the ACCESS button
-OR access it via the tutorial tab of the PDA by activating the Micro Jump Drive Activation mission.
-Follow the directions in the interface.
-Do not place any items into the Micro Jump Drive.[/sup]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][ff00ff]要使这个设备正常工作，需要在伊甸园设置菜单中启用实验功能。[-][/c]
[sup]一种实验性驱动器，它生成一个短程虫洞，使飞船向前跳跃一大段距离。只能在太空中使用，并且仅限于驾驶小型飞船(SV)或大型飞船(CV)。
放置后，应保持此设备断电状态，因为当需要时它将自动开启。
[c][FFFFFF]使用说明:
-将设备放置在飞船的前向方向，并保持微型跳跃驱动器断电。
-在太空中坐在驾驶座椅上。
-通过在飞船的控制面板中找到它并按下访问按钮，或通过激活PDA教程标签中的微型跳跃驱动器激活任务来访问跳跃驱动器的界面。
-按照界面中的指示操作。
-不要将任何物品放入微型跳跃驱动器中。[-][/c][/sup]

Chinese (simplified): 一种由外星无人机的回收部件制成的辅助处理器，用于首都舰船和基地。通过增加可用CPU来增强主要的CPU系统。\n\n[c][FFFFFF]完成任务“探险:无人机之地”后，可以在科技树中免费解锁这个方块。[-][/c]

English: A heavy plasma cannon carried by the most elite royal guards of the Zirax Empire. The weapon has a magnetic guidance system that allows the plasma projectiles to home in on the target.\nFinding ammunition for this weapon may be quite difficult.\nCannot use weapon attachments.
Chinese (simplified): 一种由兹瑞克斯帝国最精英的皇家卫队携带的重型等离子炮。这种武器拥有一个磁力引导系统，可以让等离子射弹锁定目标。\n为这种武器寻找弹药可能相当困难。\n不能使用武器附件。

English: Ammunition for the Royal Plasma Cannon. One cartridge refills the entire clip.
Chinese (simplified): 皇家等粒子加农炮的弹药. 一个就可装填整个弹匣.

English: A supporting structure required for wind turbines. Must be placed outdoors and elevated off the ground by at least 1 supporting block. Place a Wind Turbine directly on top.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]Wind Turbines take up a 5x5 space.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 用于支撑风力发电机的支撑结构. 必须放置在室外且高于地面1个支撑方块或以上. 直接将风力发电机放置于上方.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]风力发电机需要占用 5x5 的空间.[-][/c]

English:
A wind turbine that reduces power consumption by [c][00FF00]300W[-][/c] [c][abd1ff]once activated.
If below requirements are met the turbine will spin up over 60 seconds and then become[-][/c] [c][00FF00]permanently active.[-][/c]

[c][00FFFF][b]Requirements:[/b][-][/c]
[sup][c][FFFFFF]-Outdoors with no obstructions above.
-Placed on top of a wind turbine base.
-Temperature 15C to 35C (60F to 95F).
-Radiation less than 0.4 rad.
-Breathable atmosphere.
-If it gives a 'not enough light warning' raise the turbine base higher off the ground.[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]The requirements are hard coded and
cannot be changed by the Reforged Eden 2 developers.[-][/c][/sup]
Chinese (simplified):
一种风力涡轮机，一旦激活，可以减少[c][00FF00]300W[-][/c]的电力消耗。如果满足以下要求，涡轮机会在60秒内加速旋转，然后变成[c][00FF00]永久激活。[-][/c]

[c][00FFFF][b]要求:[/b][-][/c]
[sup][c][FFFFFF]-户外上方无障碍物。
-放置在风力涡轮机底座上方。
-温度15C至35C(60F至95F)。
-辐射小于0.4拉德。
-可呼吸的大气。
-如果出现“光线不足警告”，请将涡轮机底座提高离地距离。[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]这些要求是硬编码的，不能被重铸伊甸园2的开发者更改。[-][/c][/sup]

English:
[sup]A wind turbine that reduces power consumption by [c][00FF00]300W[-][/c] [c][abd1ff]once activated.
If below requirements are met the turbine will spin up over 60 seconds and then become[-][/c] [c][00FF00]permanently active.[-][/c]

[c][00FFFF][b]Requirements:[/b][-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]-Outdoors with no obstructions above.
-Placed on top of a wind turbine base.
-Temperature 15C to 35C (60F to 95F).
-Radiation less than 0.4 rad.
-Breathable atmosphere.
-If it gives a 'not enough light warning' raise the turbine base higher off the ground.[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]The requirements are hard coded and
cannot be changed by the Reforged Eden 2 developers.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[sup]一种风力涡轮机，一旦激活，可以减少[c][00FF00]300W[-][/c] [c][abd1ff]电力消耗。[-][/c]
如果满足以下要求，涡轮机会在60秒内加速旋转，然后变得[c][00FF00]永久活跃。[-][/c][/sup]

[c][00FFFF][b]要求:[/b][-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]-户外且上方无遮挡。
-放置在风力涡轮机底座上。
-温度在15C至35C(60F至95F)之间。
-辐射小于0.4拉德。
-可呼吸的大气环境。
-如果出现“光线不足警告”，请将涡轮机底座提高离地面。[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]这些要求是硬编码的，不能被重铸伊甸园2的开发者更改。[-][/c]

English:
A wind turbine designed for passive power generation on planets. Must be placed directly on top of a Wind Turbine Base.
It will spin up over 1 minute then if conditions are favorable it will provide a passive reduction in power consumption to your structure until it is removed.
Requires another source of power before it can activate.
Can not activate in extreme heat, cold, radiation, or where there is not a breathable atmosphere.
Chinese (simplified):
风力发电机被设计为用于在星球上持续获取电力. 必须被直接放置在风力发电机基座上方.
如果条件合适，它将花费一分钟来启动，并在被拆除前一直被动为建筑降低能耗.
启动时需要其他电源.
无法在极高/低温，辐射或是无法呼吸的环境中使用.

English: This wind turbine is reducing the power consumption of your structure. It will continue to operate until it is removed.
Chinese (simplified): 该风力发电机正在为建筑降低能耗，并会在被拆除前一直保持运作。

English:
A significant upgrade to wind turbines that reduces power consumption by [c][00FF00]600W.[-][/c]
[c][abd1ff]Cannot be crafted in a constructor. Only 15 advanced wind turbines can be upgraded per base. Upgrade existing active turbines with a multitool.
Cannot upgrade idle wind turbines.[-][/c]
[c][FFFF00]Advanced Wind Turbines should be downgraded with a multitool before removing to prevent loss of components.[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一种大幅升级的风力发电机，可以降低 [c][00FF00]600W[-][/c]的能耗
[c][abd1ff]无法在建造机中建造。 每个基地只能升级15个风力发电机. 用多功能建造枪进行升级.
未启动的风力发电机无法升级.[-][/c]
[c][FFFF00]拆除先进风力发电机之前最好先进行降级以防丢失部分组件.[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]使用设计图来解锁.[-][/c]

English: An empty hydroponics bay for planting specialized crops. \nAdd sprouts in an advanced constructor then place on top of a single growing plot. Requires a single grow lamp placed directly above. \nDoes not protect crops from environmental hazards.
Chinese (simplified): 可用于培育特定作物的空水培箱\n使用高级建造机来加入幼苗. 置于单个生长箱上方，并在正上方放置一个植物生长射灯即可开始生长. \n无法抵挡环境灾害

English: A hydroponics bay for growing specialized crops. Place on top of a single growing plot. Requires a single grow lamp placed directly above. \nDoes not protect crops from environmental hazards.
Chinese (simplified): 可用于培育特定作物的水培箱\n 置于单个生长箱上方，并在正上方放置一个植物生长射灯即可开始生长. \n无法抵挡环境灾害

English: Hydroponics Bay (Natural Stimulant) Ready for Harvest
Chinese (simplified): 水培箱 (天然兴奋剂) 成熟

English: Hydroponics Bay (Herbal Leaves) Ready for Harvest
Chinese (simplified): 水培箱 (草药叶) 成熟

English: Hydroponics Bay (Plant Protein) Ready for Harvest
Chinese (simplified): 水培箱 (植物蛋白) 成熟

English: Hydroponics Bay (Natural Sweetener) Ready for Harvest
Chinese (simplified): 水培箱 (天然甜味剂) 成熟
水培箱 (植物纤维) 成熟
水培箱 (翘曲水晶) 成熟

English: A holographic display of the Brotherhood of Farr symbol.\n\n[c][FFFFFF]The emitter base automatically hides itself after being on for 30 seconds. Turn holographic emitter off to reveal the emitter base.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种显示Farr兄弟会标志的全息图像。\n[c][FFFFFF]发射器底座在开启30秒后自动隐藏。关闭全息发射器以显示发射器底座。[-][/c]

English:
Place on a planetary resource deposit to automatically mine it over time.
Requires special Industrial Fuel to be inserted into the fuel slots at the top of its inventory.
Has a lower yield per hour but much greater fuel and storage capacity than standard auto mining devices.
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
置于矿床上方便可根据时间推移获取矿物.
需要消耗特殊的工业燃料包.
产率相对常规自动采矿机较低，但燃料容量和矿物储量都大大增加了.
[c][FFFFFF]通过原理图解锁。[-][/c]

English: Occasionally while mining certain deposits or asteroids you will obtain a whole piece of ore. These serve no purpose and can be trashed. This is due to a technical reason.
Chinese (simplified): 在手动挖掘时偶尔会挖出来一个矿物方块，这东西的出现是因为技术原因并且没有任何实际作用，可以直接销毁
虚空物质碎片\n[c][ff0000](需要虚空物质采集器)[-][/c]
虚空物质结晶\n[c][ff0000](需要先进虚空物质采集器)[-][/c]

English: The smelting process of this ore requires a furnace.
Chinese (simplified): 这种矿石的冶炼过程需要一个熔炉。

English: A near perfect ingot of highly processed Palladium.
Chinese (simplified): 一种接近完美的高加工度钯锭。

English: Hardened rock that cannot be removed.\n\n[c][ff0000]Internal scenario developer use only.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 无法移除的硬化岩石.\n\n[c][ff0000]场景开发者内部使用.[-][/c]

English:
[c][ffffff]Unlock Points:[-][/c] 100

This report is used for the Project Eden mission [c][00ff00]Research Unlock Points.[-][/c]

Have in your personal inventory while the mission is active and access a Research Computer on a UCH Research Vessel to complete the mission.
Can perform research at each research vessel only once.
Chinese (simplified):
[c][ffffff]解锁点数:[-][/c] 100

这份报告用于完成伊甸园计划任务 [c][00ff00]研究解锁点数.[-][/c]

任务激活时持有该物品并在UCH船舰的研究计算机处提交.

English:
An iron oxide ore commonly found in Hematite asteroids.

Certain individuals and mining corporations may be interested in this but it's not used in any known constructor recipes or commonly traded for.

Can be packaged into an Ore Shipment in the Decoration tab of your constructor for use in mining missions.

Used in Tier 1 mining missions.
Chinese (simplified):
一种在赤铁矿小行星中常见的氧化铁矿物

某些个体和公司可能会对这种矿物感兴趣，但是目前无法用于制造或是交易.

可以在建造机的装饰一栏中制造为矿物包裹，用于完成采矿任务.

用于1级采矿任务

English: A shipment of packaged Hematite Ore.\nCertain individuals in mining sites may be interested in this. Must be in your personal inventory to turn in.\nUsed in T1 Mining Missions.
Chinese (simplified): 一箱打包好的赤铁矿石\n采矿场的某些个体可能对它有兴趣. 提交时必须置于背包内.\n用于1级采矿任务.

English:
An iron-titanium oxide.

Certain individuals and mining corporations may be interested in this but it's not used in any known constructor recipes or commonly traded for.

Can be packaged into an Ore Shipment in the Decoration tab of your constructor for use in mining missions.

Used in Tier 2 mining missions.
Chinese (simplified):
一种铁-钛复合氧化物

某些个体和公司可能会对这种矿物感兴趣，但是目前无法用于制造或是交易.

可以在建造机的装饰一栏中制造为矿物包裹，用于完成采矿任务.

用于2级采矿任务

English: A shipment of packaged Ilmenite Ore.\nCertain individuals in mining sites may be interested in this. Must be in your personal inventory to turn in.\nUsed in T2 Mining Missions.
Chinese (simplified): 一箱打包好的钛铁矿石\n采矿场的某些个体可能对它有兴趣. 提交时必须置于背包内.\n用于2级采矿任务.

English:
A mineral consisting of manganese dioxide.

Certain individuals and mining corporations may be interested in this but it's not used in any known constructor recipes or commonly traded for.

Can be packaged into an Ore Shipment in the Decoration tab of your constructor for use in mining missions.

Used in Tier 3 mining missions.
Chinese (simplified):
一种含有二氧化锰的矿石

某些个体和公司可能会对这种矿物感兴趣，但是目前无法用于制造或是交易.

可以在建造机的装饰一栏中制造为矿物包裹，用于完成采矿任务.

用于3级采矿任务

English: A shipment of packaged Pyrolusite Ore.\nCertain individuals in mining sites may be interested in this. Must be in your personal inventory to turn in.\nUsed in T3 Mining Missions.
Chinese (simplified): 一箱打包好的软锰矿石\n采矿场的某些个体可能对它有兴趣. 提交时必须置于背包内.\n用于3级采矿任务.

English:
An oxide mineral composed of chromium, iron, and oxygen.

Certain individuals and mining corporations may be interested in this but it's not used in any known constructor recipes or commonly traded for.

Can be packaged into an Ore Shipment in the Decoration tab of your constructor for use in mining missions.

Used in Tier 4 mining missions.
Chinese (simplified):
一种主要成分是铬，铁以及氧的矿物

某些个体和公司可能会对这种矿物感兴趣，但是目前无法用于制造或是交易.

可以在建造机的装饰一栏中制造为矿物包裹，用于完成采矿任务.

用于4级采矿任务

English: A shipment of packaged Chromite Ore.\nCertain individuals in mining sites may be interested in this. Must be in your personal inventory to turn in.\nUsed in T4 Mining Missions.
Chinese (simplified): 一箱打包好的铬铁矿石\n采矿场的某些个体可能对它有兴趣. 提交时必须置于背包内.\n用于4级采矿任务.

English: An advanced electromagnet used in the construction of railguns and other advanced devices.
Chinese (simplified): 一种用于制造磁轨和其他先进设备的高级电磁铁

English: A device for accelerating a projectile using electromagnetism.
Chinese (simplified): 一种利用电磁效应加速投射物的设备

English: A pack of fuel suitable for the operation of heavy industrial equipment.\nCannot be used in standard fuel tanks or devices.\n[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一包用于维持重型工业设备运行的燃料.\n不能作为原版燃料使用.\n[c][FFFFFF]通过蓝图解锁.[-][/c]

English: A component used in some advanced computers.
Chinese (simplified): 一种用于高级计算机的元件

English: An extremely advanced computer used in some advanced devices.
Chinese (simplified): 一种极其先进的计算机，用于制造高端设备

English: Can be broken down into several crafting and trading components in a deconstructor. Also yields Deuterium.
Chinese (simplified): 可以在拆解机中分解为建造材料和商品，同时会产生氘

English: Can be broken down into several crafting and trading components in a deconstructor. Also yields Deuterium.
Chinese (simplified): 可以在拆解机中分解为建造材料和商品，同时会产生氘

English: Can be sold to the Trade Federation at their Distribution Headquarters.
Chinese (simplified): 可以在贸易联邦的配送总部处出售

English: Can be sold to Polaris at their Distribution Centers.
Chinese (simplified): 可以在极星的配送中心处出售

English: Can be sold to Pirates at their Distribution Centers.
Chinese (simplified): 可以在海盗的配送中心处出售

English: Can be sold to Zirax Empire at their Distribution Centers.
Chinese (simplified): 可以在兹瑞克斯帝国的配送中心处出售

English: Can be sold to the Free Colonists at their Distribution Centers.
Chinese (simplified): 可以在自由殖民者的配送中心处出售

English: Can be sold to traders or used in crafting.
Chinese (simplified): 可以出售或是用于合成

English: Used to power and cool specialized mining equipment.
Chinese (simplified): 用于驱动和冷却特定采矿设备

English: Can be processed in a deconstructor.
Used to construct advanced equipment or trading goods.
Chinese (simplified): 可以出售或是用于合成高级装备

English: Sell at a faction's Distribution Headquarters or Distribution Center.
Chinese (simplified): 在派系总部或分发中心出售。

English: A shipment of advanced components from a Trade Federation Advanced Orbital Factory in Tranquility. Sell to Polaris Orbital Robotics Factories and Optronic Orbital Factories in The Forge. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 宁静星域 的贸易联邦高级轨道工厂发送的一批先进组件。可以出售给 锻造星域 的极星轨道机器人工厂和光电工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of basic components from a Colonists Basic Orbital Factory in Prosperity. Sell to Trade Federation Advanced Orbital Factories in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 繁荣星域 的殖民者基础轨道工厂发送的一批基本组件。可以出售给 宁静星域 的贸易联邦高级轨道工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of various crops from a Colonists Orbital Hydroponics Farm in Prosperity. Sell to Polaris Orbital Breweries in The Forge or Trade Federation Orbital Food Factories in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 繁荣星域 的殖民者轨道粮食水培农场发送的一批农产品. 可以出售给 锻造星域 的极星轨道酿酒厂或是宁静星域 的贸易联邦轨道食品厂. 使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of specialized farming equipment from a Colonists Basic Orbital Factory in Prosperity. Sell to Polaris Orbital Livestock Farms in The Forge. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 繁荣星域 的殖民者基础轨道工厂发送的一批专业化农具. 可以出售给 锻造星域 的极星轨道牧场。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of specialized fertilizer from a Trade Federation Orbital Waste Facility in Tranquility. Sell to Colonists Orbital Hydroponics Farms in Prosperity. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 宁静星域 的贸易联邦轨道废物处理站发送的一批专用肥料. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者轨道水培农场。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of food products from a Trade Federation Orbital Food Factory in Tranquility. Sell to Colonists Orbital Habitats in Prosperity or Polaris Orbital Habitats in The Forge. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 宁静星域 的贸易联邦轨道食品厂发送的一批食品. 可以出售给 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者轨道聚居点或是 锻造星域 的极星轨道聚居点。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of industrial fuel from a Colonists Orbital Fuel Refinery in Prosperity or a Trade Federation Orbital Waste Facility in Tranquility. Sell to various Polaris orbital factories in The Forge. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 繁荣星域 的殖民者基础轨道工厂或是 宁静星域 的贸易联邦轨道废物处理站发送的一批燃料. 可以出售给 锻造星域 的极星轨道工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of hydrogen gas from a Trade Federation Orbital Hydrogen Harvester around a gas giant in Tranquility. Sell to Colonists Orbital Fuel Refineries in Prosperity. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 宁静星域 的贸易联邦氢气采集器(气态巨星周边)发送的一批氢气罐子. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者轨道燃料精炼厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of advanced hydroponic farming equipment from a Trade Federation Advanced Orbital Factory in Tranquility. Sell to Colonists Orbital Hydroponic Farms in Prosperity. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 宁静星域 的贸易联邦高级轨道工厂发送的一批先进水培农具. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者轨道粮食水培农场。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of industrial equipment from a Colonists Basic Orbital Factory in Prosperity. Sell to various Polaris orbital factories in The Forge. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 繁荣星域 的殖民者基础轨道工厂发送的一批工业设备. 可以出售给多个 锻造星域 的极星轨道。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of various ingots from a Polaris Orbital Refinery in The Forge or neutral space. Sell to Coloists Basic Orbital Factories in Prosperity. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 锻造星域 或 中立星域 的极星轨道精炼厂发送的一批各种矿锭. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者基础轨道工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A sealed shipment of high value jewelry from a Trade Federation Orbital Jewelry Factory. Sell to Colonists Orbital Habitats in Prosperity. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 贸易联邦的珠宝工厂发送的一批高价值封装珠宝. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者聚居地。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of high quality leather from a Polaris Orbital Livestock Farm in The Forge. Sell to Trade Federation Orbital Jewelry Factories in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 锻造星域 的极星轨道牧场发送的一批高质量皮革. 可以出售给 宁静星域 的贸易联邦的珠宝工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of various liquors from a Polaris Orbital Brewery in The Forge. Sell to Colonists Orbital Habitats in Prosperity or Trade Federation Orbital Habitats and Orbital Hotels in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 锻造星域 的极星轨道酿酒厂发送的一批各类酒水. 可以出售给繁荣星域 的殖民者聚居地或是 宁静星域 的贸易联邦聚居地以及轨道旅馆 。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of mundane livestock feed from a Colonists Orbital Hydroponics Farm in Prosperity. Sell to Polaris Orbital Livestock Farms in The Forge. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 繁荣星域 的殖民者轨道水培农场发送的一批非常普通的牲畜饲料. 可以出售给 锻造星域 的极星轨道牧场。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of frozen meats from a Polaris Orbital Livestock Farm in The Forge. Sell to Trade Federation Orbital Food Factories in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 锻造星域 的极星轨道牧场发送的一批冷冻肉类. 可以出售给 宁静星域 的贸易联邦轨道食品厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of advanced mining equipment from a Trade Federation Advanced Orbital Factory. Sell to Colonists Mining Foremen in Prosperity. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 宁静星域 的贸易联邦高级轨道工厂发送的一批先进开采设备. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者采矿工头。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of highly advanced optronics from a Polaris Optronics Factory in The Forge. Sell to Colonists Basic Orbital Factories in Prosperity or Trade Federation Advanced Orbital Factories in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 锻造星域 的极星轨道光电工厂发送的一批极为先进光电设备. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者基础轨道工厂或是 宁静星域 的贸易联邦高级轨道工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of ores from a Colonists Mining Foreman in Prosperity. Sell to Polaris Orbital Refineries in The Forge or neutral space and Orbital Alloy Smelteries in The Forge. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 繁荣星域 的殖民者采矿工头发送的一批矿石. 可以出售给 锻造星域 或 中立星域 的极星轨道精炼厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of oxygen from a Colonists Orbital Oxygen Harvester around a gas giant in Prosperity. Sell to Polaris Orbital Habitats and Orbital Livestock Farms in The Forge or to Trade Federation Orbital Habitats and Orbital Hotels in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 繁荣星域 的殖民者氧气采集器(气态巨星周边)发送的一批氧气罐子. 可以出售给 锻造星域 的极星轨道聚居地和轨道牧场或是 宁静星域 的贸易联邦聚居地以及轨道旅馆。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of rare metals from a Polaris Orbital Alloy Smeltery in The Forge. Sell to Colonists Basic Orbital Factories in Prosperity or Trade Federation Advanced Orbital Factories and Orbital Jewelry Factories in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 锻造星域 的极星轨道合金炼制厂发送的一批稀有金属. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者基础轨道工厂或是 宁静星域 的贸易联邦高级轨道工厂以及珠宝工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of highly advanced robotics from a Polaris Orbital Robotics Factory in The Forge. Sell to Trade Federation Advanced Orbital Factories and Orbital Jewelry Factories in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 锻造星域 的极星轨道机器人工厂发送的一批极为先进的机器人部件. 可以出售给 宁静星域 的贸易联邦高级轨道工厂以及珠宝工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of toxic waste from various Polaris orbital factories in The Forge. Sell to Colonists Orbital Fuel Refineries in Prosperity or Trade Federation Orbital Waste Facilities in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 由多个 锻造星域 的极星轨道工厂发送的有毒废料. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者轨道燃料精炼厂或是 宁静星域 的贸易联邦轨道废物处理站。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of water from a Polaris Orbital Water Harvester around a gas giant. Sell to Colonists Orbital Hydroponics Farms and Orbital Fuel Refineries in Prosperity or Trade Federation Orbital Food Factories and Orbital Hotels in Tranquility. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 锻造星域 的极星氧气采集器(气态巨星周边)发送的一批水桶. 可以出售给 繁荣星域 的殖民者轨道水培农场以及燃料精炼厂或是宁静星域 的贸易联邦轨道食品厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A shipment of military equipment. Sell to faction bounty offices in faction territory. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 一批军用装备. 可以出售给 对应领地中的阵营官员。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A self contained transport pod with all the basic essentials and supplies to keep a small crew of workers alive in your cargo hold. Sell to various orbital factories. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 一个独立配备所有基本必需品和补给品的运输舱，可让几个工人在其中中生存. 可以出售给多种轨道工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: A spacious transport pod with all the basic essentials and supplies to keep a small crew of officers alive in your cargo hold. Sell to various orbital factories. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 一个配备了所有基本必需品和补给品的宽敞运输舱，可让几个军官在货舱中生存. 可以出售给多种轨道工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English: An assortment of advanced polymer pellets often used in the manufacturing of plastics and other materials.
Chinese (simplified): 一种在塑料和其他材料的制造中经常使用的先进聚合物颗粒的分类。

English: A self contained transport pod with a full suite of luxury amenities for transporting the most important VIPs. Sell to various orbital factories. Use logistics toolbar to trade.
Chinese (simplified): 一个自给自足的运输舱，配备了全套豪华设施，用于运输最重要的VIP。出售给各种轨道工厂。使用物流工具栏进行交易。

English:
A sealed crate that may contain stolen supplies, military equipment, or other items.
Open using a science station on board your ship or base. The cache must be in your personal inventory.

[c][FFFF00]Connect to a cargo container with plenty of free space via logistics before opening caches.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一个密封的板条箱，可能包含被盗的补给品、军事装备或其他物品。
使用您船上或基地上的科学站打开。该缓存必须在您的个人库存中。

[c][FFFF00]在打开缓存前，通过后勤系统连接到一个拥有大量空闲空间的货物集装箱。[-][/c]

English:
A sealed crate that contains rewards equal to an equivalent alien loot container found in POIs.
Open using a science station on board your ship or base. The cache must be in your personal inventory.

[c][FFFF00]Connect to a cargo container with plenty of free space via logistics before opening caches.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一个密封的箱子，包含的奖励等同于在POIs中发现的等价外星战利品容器。
使用你的船或基地上的研究站打开。在打开储藏箱之前，它必须在你的个人库存中。

[c][FFFF00]在打开储藏箱之前，通过物流连接到一个有足够空间的货物容器。[-][/c]

English: A small focusing lens for manufacturing advanced lasers.
Chinese (simplified): 一个用于制造先进激光器的小型聚焦透镜。

English: A large focusing lens for manufacturing advanced lasers.
Chinese (simplified): 用于制造先进激光器的大型聚焦透镜。

English: A diamond that has been perfectly cut in an universal constructor.
Chinese (simplified): 在通用建造机中完美切割的钻石。\n

English: A device used for regulating the flow of energy.
Chinese (simplified): 一种用于调节能量流动的装置。

English: A survey probe containing basic scanning equipment and radio transmitters.\nUsed only for missions or can be sold to UCH Research Vessels.\nOne use only.
Chinese (simplified): 一个包含基本扫描设备和无线电发射器的调查探测器。\n仅用于任务或可以出售给UCH研究飞船。\n仅限一次使用。

English: A survey probe containing scientific instruments and long range radio transmitters.\nUsed only for missions or can be sold to UCH Research Vessels.\nOne use only.
Chinese (simplified): 一个装有科学仪器和远程无线电发射器的探测器。\n仅用于任务或可以出售给UCH研究船。\n仅限一次使用。

English: A survey probe containing advanced sensors and subspace transmitters.\nUsed only for missions or can be sold to UCH Research Vessels.\nOne use only.
Chinese (simplified): 一个包含先进传感器和太空传送器的探测器。\n仅用于任务或可以出售给UCH研究飞船。\n仅限一次使用。
高科技系统调查探测器

English: A survey probe containing highly sophisticated scientific instruments and long range subspace antenna.\nUsed only for missions or can be sold to UCH Research Vessels.\nOne use only.
Chinese (simplified): 一个装有高度复杂的科学仪器和长距离太空天线的探测器。\n仅用于任务或可以出售给UCH研究船。\n仅限一次使用。

English:
A kit containing everything needed for a damaged ship to repair vital systems. 
One use only.

Turn in to captains of damaged vessels or sell to traders.
Chinese (simplified):
一个工具包，包含受损飞船修复重要系统所需的一切。
仅限一次使用。

交给受损飞船的船长或卖给商人。

English: A survey report on various spacial anomalies, wrecks, or other objects of interest. UCH Research Vessels may be interested in this.
Chinese (simplified): 一份关于各种空间异常、残骸或其他令人感兴趣兴趣的物体的调查报告。 UCH研究船可能对此感兴趣。

English: A survey report of asteroids, gasses, and interstellar dust. Mining Foremen on deep space mining vessels may be interested in this.
Chinese (simplified): 小行星、气体和星际尘埃的调查报告。 深空采矿船上的采矿工头可能对此感兴趣。

English: A survey report of wrecks, weapon signatures, and subspace communications. Bounty hunter offices may be interested in this.
Chinese (simplified): 残骸、武器特征和亚空间通信的调查报告。 赏金猎人办公室可能对此感兴趣。

English: Used to activate a geothermal generator on a planet with high geological activity.\nPlace in a connected container and use the upgrade function of a multitool on a geothermal generator to activate it.\nThe core sample is too heavy to lift via ship and will quickly cool into a pile of unusable stone.
Chinese (simplified): 用于在多地质活动的行星上激活地热发电机.\n放入连接的容器中并用多功能工具枪的升级功能来激活地热发电机.\n岩芯样本实在是太重以至于无法用飞船运输，且会很快冷却成一堆无法没有卵用的石头.

English: Salvaged part from an alien Drone used in the construction of computational devices.
Chinese (simplified): 从外星无人机上打捞到的部件，用于制造计算设备

English: A very rare AI core from an alien Drone used in the construction of advanced devices.
Chinese (simplified): 一颗从外星无人机上打捞到的极其稀有的AI核心，用于高端设备制造

English:
Time reduction: [c][FFFFFF]30 minutes[-][/c] 

Uses 3D printing to help manufacture base components. 

When inserted into the blueprint factory it reduces build time of the current blueprint. 

Can only be added to blueprints that are still missing components.

当插入蓝图工厂时它会缩减当前蓝图的建造时间.

Time reduction: [c][FFFFFF]2 hours[-][/c] 

Uses advanced technology to 3D print blocks or devices using a stream of nanites. 

When inserted into the blueprint factory it reduces build time of the current blueprint. 

Can only be added to blueprints that are still missing components.

时间减少: [c][FFFFFF]2 小时[-][/c] 

使用大量纳米机器人来对方块和设备进行3D打印. 

当插入蓝图工厂时它会缩减当前蓝图的建造时间. 

只能被用于仍缺失组件的蓝图.
