English: A medical injector that injects nanites directly into the bloodstream to stimulate regeneration. \n\nGrants slow health regeneration for 15 minutes.
Chinese (simplified): 一种医疗注射器，将纳米机器人直接注入血管以刺激再生。\n\n持续15分钟的缓慢生命值恢复。

English: A medical injector that injects nanites directly into the bloodstream to stimulate regeneration. \n\nGrants fast health regeneration for 2 minutes.
Chinese (simplified): 一种医疗注射器，将纳米机器人直接注入血液，以刺激身体再生。\n持续2分钟的快速生命值恢复。

English:
A medical injector that injects nanites directly into the bloodstream to stimulate stamina recovery. 

Grants slow stamina regeneration for 15 minutes.
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种医疗注射器，将纳米机器人直接注入血液，以刺激体力恢复。\n持续15分钟的缓慢体力恢复。\n[c][FFFFFF]通过图纸解锁。[-][/c]

English:
A medical injector that injects nanites directly into the bloodstream to stimulate stamina recovery. 

Grants fast stamina regeneration for 2 minutes.
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种医疗注射器，将纳米机器人直接注入血液，以刺激体力恢复。\n持续2分钟的快速体力恢复。\n[c][FFFFFF]通过图纸解锁。[-][/c]

English: Injects radiation cleaning nanites into the bloodstream slowly lowering body radiation. \n\nGrants slow radiation reduction for 15 minutes. Does not prevent or cure any radation illness.
Chinese (simplified): 注入清除辐射的纳米机器人进入血液，缓慢降低体内的辐射水平。\n持续15分钟的缓慢辐射减少效果。不能预防或治疗任何辐射疾病。

English: When consumed encases the user in a nearly impenetrable forcefield protecting from virtually all damage for 30 seconds. \n\nSufficently powerful attacks can still kill the user.
Chinese (simplified): 消耗后会在用户周围形成一个几乎无法穿透的力场，保护用户免受几乎所有伤害，持续30秒。\n足够强大的攻击仍然可能导致用户死亡。

English:
A potent beverage that grants increased stamina regeneration at the cost of health for 5 minutes. Use with caution.
[c][FFFFFF]Schematic required to unlock.[-][/c] 

[i][c][A9A9A9]Another fine brew developed by Appleseed Corporation.[-][/c][/i]

[i][c][A9A9A9]Another fine brew developed by Appleseed Corporation.[-][/c][/i]

English: An emergency life support and medical consumable of alien origin. \n\nFully refills all suit stats and stabilizes radiation. Cures most ailments. Single use only.
Chinese (simplified): 一种外星起源的紧急生命支持和医疗消耗品。\n完全重新填满所有服装属性，并稳定辐射。治愈大多数疾病。仅限单次使用。

English: A portable oxygen tank used for refilling suit oxygen. \nNot compatible with refilling ship or base O2 tanks.
Chinese (simplified): 一个用于为护甲充氧的便携式氧气瓶.\n无法为建筑或载具氧气瓶充氧

English:
[c][FF5555]Restores 100 health immediately and another 100 health over 10 seconds.[-][/c]
An upgrade to the standard bandage that binds wounds and rapidly accelerates healing.

[c][00FF00]Use from the toolbar with LMB or from Inventory with Shift+RMB[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][FF5555]立即恢复100生命值，接下来的10秒内再恢复100生命值。[-][/c]
对标准绷带的升级，可以绑定伤口并迅速加速愈合过程。

[c][00FF00]使用左键点击工具栏或使用Shift+右键点击库存来使用。[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF]通过图纸解锁。[-][/c]

English:
A plasma rifle of Abyssal design. 

Rapidly fires superheated plasma orbs bound within a magnetic field.
Shares weapon attachments with the Plasma Cannon.
Chinese (simplified): 一种深渊设计的等离子步枪。\n快速发射被束缚在磁场中的超热等离子球体。\n与等离子炮共享武器配件。

English: A laser rifle of Abyssal design.\nShares weapon attachments with the Laser Rifle.
Chinese (simplified): 一种深渊设计的激光步枪。\n与激光步枪共享武器配件。

English:
Fires a short range jet of super cold exotic plasma. 

Applies cryoshock to enemy players slowing their movement speed and lowering their body temperature.
Cannot use weapon attachments.
Chinese (simplified): 发射一股短程超冷的异种等离子体。\n对敌方玩家施加冰冻冲击，减缓他们的移动速度并降低他们的体温。\n不能使用武器配件。

English:
A plasma cell of Abyssal design used in Entropic Weapons. 
Refills entire magazine. 

Can be broken down into Promethium Pellets in a deconstructor.
Chinese (simplified): 一种深渊设计的等离子电池，用于熵增武器。\n重新填满整个弹匣。\n可以在解构器中分解成钷颗粒。

English:
A minigun that fires a burst of incendiary grenades for large area of effect damage to soft targets. 

Wears out quickly.
[c][FFFFFF]Unlocked via schematic.[-][/c]
Cannot use weapon attachments.
Chinese (simplified):
一种迷你枪，发射一连串的燃烧榴弹，对软目标造成大面积的伤害效果。
很快就会磨损。
[c][FFFFFF]通过图纸解锁。[-][/c]
不能使用武器配件。

English:
A double barrel shotgun capable of quickly firing off two rounds at point blank range. Effective at very close range only.
The adrenaline from using this weapon restores 25 stamina per shot.
Shares weapon attachments with the Combat Shotgun.

[i][c][A9A9A9]Rip and tear...[-][/c][/i]
Chinese (simplified):
一种双管霰弹枪，能够在极近距离迅速发射两发子弹。仅在非常近的距离内有效。
使用这种武器时的肾上腺素每发子弹可恢复25点体力。
与战斗霰弹枪共享武器配件。

[i][c][A9A9A9]撕裂……[-][/c][/i]

English:
An experimental light railgun rifle capable of inflicting massive damage to soft targets or light damage to structures. 

Has an enhanced targeting system allowing for night vision while helmet is equipped. Toggle with suit light hot key. 

1500 damage per shot before resistance modifiers.
Cannot use weapon attachments.
Chinese (simplified):
一种实验性的轻型轨道炮步枪，能够对软目标造成巨大伤害，或对结构造成轻微伤害。
拥有一个增强的瞄准系统，在佩戴头盔时允许使用夜视功能。通过服装灯光热键切换。
在抗性修正之前，每发子弹造成1500点伤害。
不能使用武器配件。

English: An experimental ion blaster that fires ionized bolts that deal increased damage to shields, devices, and mechanical entities.\nShares weapon attachments with the Laser Rifle.
Chinese (simplified): 一种实验性的离子爆破器，发射离子化弹丸，对护盾、设备和机械实体造成增加的伤害。\n与激光步枪共享武器配件。

English:
An experimental lightning gun designed by X-Corp. Deals heavy damage in close range. Deals bonus damage to mechanical entities.

Use right click to overload the rifle, creating a deadly short range blast.
Cannot use weapon attachments.
Chinese (simplified):
一种由X-Corp设计的实验性电击枪。在近距离内造成重大伤害。对机械实体造成额外伤害。

使用右键使步枪过载，产生致命的短程爆炸。
不能使用武器配件。

English: An experimental plasma rifle designed by X-Corp.\n[c][ffff00]A flaw in the design does not allow this weapon to be reloaded.[-][/c]\nCannot use weapon attachments.
Chinese (simplified): 一种由X-Corp设计的实验性等离子步枪。\n[c][ffff00]设计上的缺陷不允许这种武器重新装填。[-][/c]\n不能使用武器配件。

English: A plasma cartridge for the X-Corp PR-65A Plasma Rifle.\nFully recharges the rifle.
Chinese (simplified): 一种用于X-Corp PR-65A等离子步枪的等离子弹夹。\n完全重新充能步枪。

English: You are suffering from the effects of prolonged cryosleep.
Chinese (simplified): 你正遭受长期冷冻睡眠的影响。

English: You're not sure where you are or even who you are.
Chinese (simplified): 你不确定自己在哪里，甚至不知道自己是谁。

English: Colonized areas of space. Affects what factions you will find there.
Chinese (simplified): 已被殖民的区域，决定了你可能见到的派系

English: Alien drones of unknown origin. Hostile.

[c][D5D5D5]Savanth has been a thorn in the side of the Free Colonists for a number of years. Responsible for a number of bandit attacks on shipping lanes, he has now stepped up his attacks to include stations and civilian outposts.
The Free Colonists will pay for proof of his demise, although it is often not long until he returns in a freshly cloned body.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][FFFFFF][b]通缉方:[/b][-][/c] [c][4CA5FF]自由殖民者(Free Colonists)[-][/c]
[c][FFFFFF][b]隶属于:[/b][-][/c] [c][BF0000]强盗(Bandits)[-][/c]
将其带到殖民者领土内交易站区的赏金猎人办公室领取奖励。

[c][D5D5D5]萨万斯多年来一直是自由殖民者(Free Colonists)的眼中钉。他负责多次针对航运路线的强盗(Bandits)袭击，现在他的袭击已经升级，包括对站点和平民前哨的攻击。
自由殖民者(Free Colonists)将为他的死亡证据支付报酬，尽管他经常不久就会在一个新克隆的身体中回来。[-][/c]

English:

Bring to a Bounty Hunter Office in trading station sectors in Colonists territory for a reward.

[c][D5D5D5]Suspected of being a terrorist leader in the pirate gang known as the Bloodhunters, Marko made a name for himself for his extreme tactics.
He is wanted for his involvement in the asteroid bombardment of Intrazia Prime.[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
[c][FFFFFF][b]通缉方:[/b][-][/c] [c][4CA5FF]自由殖民者(Free Colonists)[-][/c]

将其带到殖民者领土内交易站区的赏金猎人办公室领取奖励。

[c][D5D5D5]怀疑是被称为血猎者的海盗团伙中的恐怖主义领袖，马克以他的极端战术而声名狼藉。
他因参与对Intrazia Prime的小行星轰炸而遭到通缉。[-][/c]

Bring to a Bounty Hunter Office in trading station sectors in Colonists territory for a reward.

[c][D5D5D5]Small Tony runs a local bandit gang and has frequently been spotted hiding out in derelict space stations.
Thought to have been killed more often than any other bandit, he keeps coming back for more thanks to his clone chamber which no one has been able to find.
The Free Colonists would pay well for anyone who can add one more death to his name.[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]小托尼经营着一个当地的强盗(Bandits)团伙，经常有人发现他藏身在废弃的空间站里。
他被认为比任何其他强盗(Bandits)被杀的次数都多，但由于他的克隆室，没有人能找到，他不断回来。
自由殖民者(Free Colonists)愿意为能给他的名字上再添一笔死亡的人支付丰厚的报酬。[-][/c]

[c][D5D5D5]Savanth has been a thorn in the side of the Free Pirates for a number of years. Responsible for a number of bandit attacks on shipping lanes, he has now stepped up his attacks to include stations and civilian outposts.
The Free Pirates will pay for proof of his demise, although it is often not long until he returns in a freshly cloned body.[-][/c]

自由海盗将为他的死亡证据支付报酬，尽管他经常不久就会在一个新克隆的身体中回来。[-][/c]

The Free Pirates would pay well for anyone who can add one more death to his name.[-][/c]

English:
A data pad containing the communication frequency of a specific trading station or factory. Can be used to help locate the factory.

[c][00FFFF]Requirements:[-][/c]
[sup][c][FFFFFF]-Must be friendly with Trade Federation.
-Must be in personal toolbar to initially activate the mission then can be stored in cargo.
-If you have changed playfields or restarted the game move any item into or out of your inventory to update the PDA.
-Activate the tracking mission under PDA > Trading.
-Place the required scanning probe in your personal toolbar.
-As long as the mission is currently active you will get a notification on your HUD if you enter a playfield that contains the factory you are tracking.
-Does not pinpoint the exact location, only whether or not it exists in your current planet, moon, or sector to save time having to fully explore the area.
-The trading frequency is reusable and can be activated again in the PDA.[/sup][-][/c]
Chinese (simplified):
一个数据板，包含特定交易站或工厂的通信频率。可以用来帮助定位工厂。

[c][00FFFF]要求:[-][/c]
[sup][c][FFFFFF]-必须与贸易联盟保持友好关系。
-必须在个人工具栏中才能最初激活任务，之后可以存放在货物中。
-如果你更换了游戏场地或重新启动了游戏，将任何物品移入或移出你的库存以更新PDA。
-在PDA > 贸易下激活追踪任务。
-将所需的扫描探针放在你的个人工具栏中。
-只要任务当前处于激活状态，如果你进入包含你正在追踪的工厂的游戏场地，你将在你的HUD上收到通知。
-不会精确定位具体位置，只会告诉你它是否存在于你当前的行星、卫星或扇区，以节省完全探索该区域的时间。
-交易频率可重复使用，可以在PDA中再次激活。[-][/c][/sup]

English: Welcome to our research vessel. What brings you all the way out here to {0}? As for us we are currently studying a nearby star cluster.
Chinese (simplified): 欢迎来到我们的研究船。是什么风把你吹到{0}这里来的？至于我们，目前我们正在研究附近的一个恒星团。

English: Welcome to my research vessel. We are currently performing research on the star in this system. If you have any questions I'd be happy to answer them, but please don't take up too much of my crew's time as they are behind schedule.
Chinese (simplified): 欢迎来到我的研究船。我们目前正在对这个星系中的恒星进行研究。如果你有任何问题，我很乐意回答，但请不要占用我船员太多时间，因为他们已经落后于计划了。

English: Hello. We are here in {0} performing scans of nearby planets in hopes of setting up a mining outpost.
Chinese (simplified): 你好。我们在{0}这里对附近行星进行扫描，希望建立一个采矿前哨站。

English: Welcome aboard. I am the captain of this research vessel. You will have to excuse us as we are quite busy running scans on interstellar gases and anomalies.
Chinese (simplified): 欢迎上船。我是这艘研究船的船长。我们目前正在忙于对星际气体和异常现象进行扫描，所以请见谅。

English: -Then run it again! The diagnostic must have missed something!\nOh, hi, I didn't see you there. We were recently attacked by a Zirax Battlecarrier so we have a lot of repairs left to do.
Chinese (simplified): 那就再运行一次！诊断肯定漏掉了一些东西！\n哦，你好，我没看到你在那里。我们最近被兹瑞克斯战斗航母攻击了，所以我们还有很多修理工作要做。

English: We're currently scanning for resources in {0}. Is there something I can help you with?
Chinese (simplified): 我们目前正在{0}扫描资源。有什么我可以帮忙的吗？

English: Welcome to our research vessel. What brings you all the way out here to {0}? As for us we are currently studying a nearby star cluster.
Chinese (simplified): 欢迎来到我们的研究船。是什么风把你吹到{0}这里来的？至于我们，目前我们正在研究附近的一个恒星团。

English: I came to {0} looking for work. What about you?
Chinese (simplified): 我来到{0}是来找工作的。你呢？

English: I can't wait to get myself a Bloody Zirax.
Chinese (simplified): 我迫不及待地想弄到一杯血腥兹瑞克斯。

English: The view from {0} is quite beautiful, wouldn't you say?
Chinese (simplified): 从{0}看风景真是美极了，不是吗？

English: You can meet so many interesting people in places like this.
Chinese (simplified): 在这样的地方你可以遇到很多有趣的人。

English: Many do not like the Zirax Empire but I think they bring order and stability to the galaxy.
Chinese (simplified): 许多人不喜欢兹瑞克斯帝国，但我认为他们给银河系带来了秩序和稳定。

English: Polaris has good prices but poor quality merchandise. On the other hand, the Trade Federation's products are always top quality but are too expensive for my budget. What should I do?
Chinese (simplified): 北极星的价格很好，但商品质量差。另一方面，贸易联盟的产品总是最高品质的，但对我来说太贵了。我该怎么办？

English: I heard an idiot keep insisting that TOP brewery makes root beer! That stuff has enough alcohol to degrease an engine!\nI know for a fact that you can treat infected wounds and dermal parasites with it!
Chinese (simplified): 我听说有个白痴一直坚称TOP酿酒厂生产的是根汁啤酒！那东西的酒精含量足以去油污！\n我知道实际上可以用它来治疗感染的伤口和皮肤寄生虫！

English: I hear someone talking about a new simulation today, it's called Project Eden and they say it is great!
Chinese (simplified): 我听说今天有人在谈论一个新的模拟游戏，叫做伊甸园计划，他们说非常棒！

English: I'm tired of life on this station. Maybe I should sign up for one of the colonies in the outer reaches?
Chinese (simplified): 我厌倦了在空间站的生活。也许我应该报名参加外域的某个殖民地？

English: Why are there so few variants of alien life in this galaxy? You'd expect to see at least something different on each planet!
Chinese (simplified): 为什么这个银河系中外星生命的形式这么少？你可能会期待在每个星球上至少看到一些不同的东西！

English: Have you heard of Discord? I heard they're a music group from Baymax 6.
Chinese (simplified): 你听说过Discord吗？我听说他们是来自Baymax 6的乐队。

English: I heard strange noises coming from a vent on the last colony I visited, I couldn't sleep at all.
Chinese (simplified): 我上次访问的最后一个殖民地，从通风口传来了奇怪的声音，我根本无法入睡。

English: I can't wait to ship out of this dump. The goons from HabSec keep conducting random searches on my bags. It's clearly discrimination!
Chinese (simplified): 我迫不及待地想离开这个垃圾场。HabSec的暴徒们一直在对我的包进行随机搜查。这显然是歧视！

English: A lot of people complain about the Zirax's governing. Honestly, I think they're fine. They could've regressed into complete tyranny but have kept to their treaties and keep the galaxy safe.
Chinese (simplified): 很多人抱怨兹瑞克斯的统治。说实话，我觉得他们还不错。他们本可以退回到完全的暴政，但却遵守了他们的条约，并保持了银河系的安全。

English: I've heard that Vermillion of Forge Aerospace has been contracted by Rados to build new bases for them. He has an apartment on one of the trade stations, but I don't know which.
Chinese (simplified): 我听说Forge Aerospace的Vermillion被Rados雇佣来为他们建造新的基地。他在某个贸易站有公寓，但我不知道是哪个。

English: I'm looking for a ship to Farpoint Station. Are you a Federation captain? No? Oh well.
Chinese (simplified): 我在寻找一艘前往Farpoint Station的船。你是联邦的船长吗？不是？哦，好吧。

English: I saw an idiot flying a Naginata the other day. I suppose crashing is probably the better term. Smashed right into the ground outside an Abyssal fortress on a Plasma planet!
Chinese (simplified): 我前几天看到一个白痴在飞Naginata。我想“坠毁”可能是更准确的词。他直接撞到了一个Abyssal堡垒外的等离子行星地面上！

English: Heard pirates have started holding freighter captains hostage and demanding ransom!
Chinese (simplified): 听说海盗们开始扣押货船船长作为人质，要求赎金！

English: Have you thought about bounty hunting? There are those who will pay well for bandit and raider insignias.
Chinese (simplified): 你有考虑过成为赏金猎人吗？有人愿意为强盗和掠夺者的徽章支付丰厚的报酬。

English: These new plasma turbines by Forge Aerospace are an amazing invention! They turn your generator's plasma exhaust into free power.
Chinese (simplified): Forge Aerospace公司新出的等离子涡轮机真是一项惊人的发明！它们可以将发电机的等离子废气转化为免费电力。

English: The hours are long but the pay is fair.
Chinese (simplified): 工作时间很长，但报酬是公平的。

English: I lost my access card again. HabSec is sure to flag me.
Chinese (simplified): 我又丢了访问卡。HabSec肯定会标记我。

English: You're one of those Terrans, aren't you? You're shorter than I expected.
Chinese (simplified): 你是那些地球人之一，对吧？你比我预期的要矮。

English: I just modified my pistol at a weapon locker to increase its damage.
Chinese (simplified): 我刚刚在武器柜上改进了我的手枪，以增加它的伤害力。

English: Have you seen those new effect projectors? They look so cool!
Chinese (simplified): 你看到那些新的特效投影仪了吗？它们看起来太酷了！

English: There's too many advertisements now if you ask me.
Chinese (simplified): 如果你问我，现在广告太多了。

English: Watch out for shield penetration. Weapons have become deadlier and gone are the days you could sit in place and take no damage.
Chinese (simplified): 小心护盾穿透。武器变得更致命了，你不能坐在那里不受伤的日子已经过去了。

English: I heard Polaris mining foremen are always looking for help.
Chinese (simplified): 我听说北极星矿业的工头总是在寻找帮助。

English: Mining contracts from U.I.M. are easy money.
Chinese (simplified): U.I.M.的采矿合同是容易赚的钱。

English: I have a long day ahead of me so forgive me if I don't stay and chat.
Chinese (simplified): 我今天有漫长的一天，所以如果我不留下来聊天，请原谅我。

English: I came to {0} looking for work. What about you?
I miss the forests of my homeworld. I'm trying to save up enough money to visit.
Chinese (simplified): 我想念我的母星上的森林。我正试图攒够钱去拜访。

English: My access card is broken again.
I'd watch out for pickpockets if I were you.
Chinese (simplified): 如果我是你，我会小心扒手。

English: Don't see many of your kind around here.
Chinese (simplified): 这里不常看到你这样的人。

English: What brings you to the Badlands? Nevermind, I don't want to know. Nobody ever has a good reason to come out here.
Chinese (simplified): 你来荒地有什么事？算了，我不想知道。来这里的人从来没有什么好理由。

English: I ran out of job prospects in Prosperity so I came here looking for work. Found only trouble.
Chinese (simplified): 我在繁荣之地用尽了工作机会，所以我来到这里寻找工作。找到的只有麻烦。

English: Heed my advice and stay away from upstairs.
Chinese (simplified): 听从我的建议，远离楼上。

English: These games are rigged. I know because I'm the one who rigged them.
Chinese (simplified): 这些游戏是被操纵的。我知道，因为我就是操纵它们的人。

English: Bring out yer dead! Bring out yer dead!
Chinese (simplified): 把你的死者抬出来！把你的死者抬出来！

English: I'm concerned with how fast the Syndicate has been expanding. Pretty soon there will be no more room for small time smugglers like myself. I mean, my totally legit cargo hauling business.
Chinese (simplified): 我对辛迪加扩张的速度感到担忧。很快，像我这样的小规模走私者就没有空间了。我的意思是，我完全合法的货物运输业务。

English: Keep to yourself and nobody will bother you.
Chinese (simplified): 管好你自己，就不会有人来烦你。

English: You best keep walking, tough guy.
You want to buy some death sticks?
If you're looking for work I hear Underground Music is looking for a courier.
Chinese (simplified): 如果你在找工作，我听说地下音乐正在寻找一名信使。
...塞特什守卫的鼻子在滴水。哈哈哈哈哈哈哈哈！

English: I don't know you and I don't want to know you.
Chinese (simplified): 我不认识你，也不想认识你。

English: I used to be an  adventurer like you then I took a look at my life and turned it around.
Chinese (simplified): 我曾经像你一样是个冒险家，然后我审视了自己的生活并改变了它。

English: No one here is exactly what they appear.
Chinese (simplified): 这里没有人是他们表面上看起来的那样。

English: Smuggler? Pirate? Slaver? Drug dealer? Which are you?
Chinese (simplified): 走私者？海盗？奴隶贩子？毒品贩子？你是哪一种？

English: I heard the Syndicate is ran by someone they call The Raven.
Chinese (simplified): 我听说辛迪加是由一个他们称作“乌鸦”的人掌控的。

English: I-I don't w-w-want any trouble pl-please!
Chinese (simplified): 我...我不...不想惹麻烦，拜...拜托了！

English: Have you heard the good word of Farr?
Enjoying your visit to this freeport?
Chinese (simplified): 你喜欢这次自由港的旅程吗？

English: Stay away from gas clouds in space.
There's been a lot more smugglers coming through here lately. Something is going on.
Chinese (simplified): 最近这里来了很多走私者。一定有什么事在发生。

English: Music? Entertainment? Food and drink? The Freeport here in {0} has it all!
Chinese (simplified): 音乐？娱乐？食物和饮料？这个在 {0} 的自由港应有尽有！

English: I really, really hate it here in {0}.
Chinese (simplified): 狗屎，{0} 这里真的很讨厌！

English: If you're not paying me stay away from me.
Chinese (simplified): 如果你不打算付钱，那就离我远点。

English: No one comes here by accident. Why are you here, friend?
Chinese (simplified): 没有人偶然来到这里。你来这儿，朋友，有什么事吗？

English: Take my advice and don't make the guards angry.
Chinese (simplified): 听我一句劝，别惹守卫生气。

English: Colonist stations are popping up all over. Ripe for the raiding!
Chinese (simplified): 殖民者站正在各地涌现。正是掠夺的好时机！

English: You want to have a go at me?
Did you hear what happened in the Sea of Silence?
Chinese (simplified): 你听说沉默之海发生了什么吗？

English: A group from the Omicron Raiders came through here last week. Roudy bunch but tipped good. Guess they got a good haul.
Chinese (simplified): 上周一群Omicron掠夺者从这里经过。粗鲁的一群人，但给了不错的小费。

English: You look like you could use a drink. Head on over to PAX Purgatory.
Chinese (simplified): 你看起来可能需要喝一杯。去PAX炼狱吧。

English: Keep a tight grip on your coin purse.
There's a secret way into the VIP lounge. No, I won't tell you where it is.
Chinese (simplified): 有一个秘密通道可以进入VIP休息室。不，我不会告诉你它在哪里。

English: Have a question about Reforged Eden 2 or need support on the scenario? See the [c][00FFFF]Reforged Eden 2[-][/c] workshop!\nIf playing on a server contact your server admin.
Chinese (simplified): 00、关于重铸伊甸园2的问题或需要场景支持？请查看[c][00FFFF]重铸伊甸园2[-][/c]工坊！如果是在服务器上玩，请与您的服务器管理员联系。

English: Use the logistics system to transfer blocks and items too large to fit in your personal inventory.
Chinese (simplified): 01、使用物流系统来转移过大而无法放入个人库存的方块和物品。

English: Upgrade your warp drive or collect navigational data to increase the maximum range you can warp.
Chinese (simplified): 02、升级你的翘曲引擎或收集导航数据，以增加你可以翘曲的最大范围。

English: Combat sites are an excellent source of insignias that can be turned in at a faction's bounty office inside their galactic territory.
Chinese (simplified): 03、战斗地点是获取徽章的绝佳来源，这些徽章可以在派系的银河领土内的赏金办公室上交。

English: Help friendly miners in mining sites for lucrative rewards.
Chinese (simplified): 04、在采矿地点帮助友好的矿工，可以获得丰厚的奖励。

English: Hack into data vaults or salvage wrecks in exploration sites.
Chinese (simplified): 05、侵入数据金库或在探索地点回收残骸。

English: Explore asteroid fields to discover hidden resource asteroids.
Chinese (simplified): 06、探索小行星带以发现隐藏的资源小行星。

English: Star class and faction territory can affect what you will find in a star system.
Chinese (simplified): 07、恒星的类别和派系领土可能会影响你在星系中会发现的东西。

English: Some resources can only be found in certain territories or galactic regions.\nCheck the Empyriopedia in the PDA for more information.
Chinese (simplified): 08、一些资源只能在特定的领土或银河区域找到。查看PDA中的Empyriopedia以获取更多信息。

English: Tooltips on blocks and items contain vital information on their use and the Empyiopedia in the PDA contains useful information on the scenario and is filled in as you progress.
Chinese (simplified): 09、方块和物品的提示包含有关其用途的重要信息，PDA中的Empyiopedia包含有关场景的有用信息，并且随着你的进展会不断填充。

English: Not all missions are tracked in your PDA.\nSometimes following clues will lead you to hidden treasure.
Chinese (simplified): 10、不是所有的任务都会在你的PDA中被追踪。\n有时跟随线索会引导你找到隐藏的宝藏。

English: You continue to earn unlock points after level 25 through missions and turning in valuable items.
Chinese (simplified): 11、即使在达到25级之后，你仍然可以通过完成任务和上交有价值的物品来获得解锁点数。

English: Schematics can unlock powerful crafting recipes or be sold for credits.
Chinese (simplified): 12、图纸可以解锁强大的制造配方，或者可以出售以换取信用点。

English: UCH Research Vessels provide useful services such as managing warp drive upgrades and unlocking schematics.\nThey can typically only be found in neutral territory.
Chinese (simplified): 13、UCH研究飞船提供有用的服务，如管理翘曲引擎升级和解锁图纸。它们通常只能在中立领土找到。

English: The major regions of the galaxy are The Throne, The Forge, Tranquility, Prosperity, The Wastelands, Solitude, Sea of Silence, The Badlands, Nexus, The Dronelands, and Decay.
Chinese (simplified): 14、银河系的主要区域包括宝座、熔炉、宁静之地、繁荣之地、荒原、孤独之地、沉默之海、不毛之地、纽带之地、无人机之地和衰败之地。

English: Scanning stations and science stations are useful equipment for exploration vessels.
Chinese (simplified): 15、扫描站和科学站是探索飞船的有用设备。

English: Helping those in need can improve your reputation with a faction.
Chinese (simplified): 16、帮助那些需要帮助的人可以提高你在某个派系中的声望。

English: Passive power options such as solar panels, wind turbines, geothermal generators, or plasma turbines can improve or even eliminate fuel use.
Chinese (simplified): 17、可选的被动式电力设备，如太阳能板、风力涡轮机、地热发电机或等离子涡轮机，可以改善甚至消除燃料使用。

English: Improve your shields by adding shield upgrades.\nBe careful, some weapons have shield penetration.
Chinese (simplified): 18、通过添加护盾升级，提高你的护盾性能。\n小心，有些武器具有护盾穿透能力。

English: You can increase your maximum CPU by adding more CPU extenders.
Chinese (simplified): 19、你可以通过增加更多的CPU扩展器来增加你的最大CPU。

English: There is a maximum number of light, medium, or heavy weapons you can have on a single ship or base.
Chinese (simplified): 20、单一飞船或基地上，轻型、中型或重型武器的数量是有最大限制的。

English: You can upgrade a smaller thruster to a higher tier rather than replacing it with a larger thruster.
Chinese (simplified): 21、你可以将小型推进器升级到更高的级别，而不是用更大的推进器替换它。

English: Using a dedicated mining vessel is much faster than mining by hand.
Chinese (simplified): 22、使用专门的采矿飞船比手工采矿要快得多。

English: Add that finishing touch with decorative blocks such as effect projectors or lcd screens.
Chinese (simplified): 23、使用装饰性区块，如效果投影仪或液晶屏，为建筑添加最后的润色。

English: You can pay freighters to complete some jobs for you at a GIN console.
Chinese (simplified): 24、你可以在GIN控制台聘请货船来为你完成一些工作。

English: Sometimes you can find hackable satellites near a star.\nThese can be hacked into without a reputation penalty and can yield valuable reports and other rewards.
Chinese (simplified): 25、有时候你可以在恒星附近找到可以被黑客攻击的卫星。\n这些卫星可以在不损害声望的情况下被黑客攻击，并且可以提供有价值的报告和其他奖励。

English: Before charging headfirst into an unfamiliar foe, take time to look them over from a safe distance.\nDon't try to engage dreadnoughts in a starting ship! Or do, it's a free galaxy.
Chinese (simplified): 26、在不顾一切地冲向一个不熟悉的敌人之前，先花时间从安全的距离观察它们。\n不要试图用起始飞船去攻击无畏舰！或者，试试吧，反正这是一个自由的银河系。

English: Check a planet's gravity before trying to land otherwise your landing might be permanent.
Chinese (simplified): 27、在尝试着陆之前检查一个星球的重力，否则你的着陆可能是永久性的。

English: The damage protection of your armor is reduced based on how much durability it's missing.\nKeep your armor repaired!
Chinese (simplified): 29、你的护甲的损伤保护会根据其缺失的耐久度而减少。保持你的护甲维修！

English: Some resources such as rich asteroids require specialized mining equipment.
Chinese (simplified): 30、一些资源，如富集小行星，需要专门的采矿设备。

English: [c][FFFF00]Kinetic weapons[-][/c] such as cannons and railguns do better versus exposed blocks.\n[c][00ffff]Energy weapons[-][/c] such as lasers do better versus shields.
Chinese (simplified): [c][FFFF00]动能武器[-][/c] 如大炮和电磁炮，在对抗暴露区块时表现更佳。\n[c][00ffff]能量武器[-][/c] 如激光，在对抗护盾时表现更佳。

English: Guns can be improved by attaching mods using a weapon locker.
Chinese (simplified): 32、枪械可以通过在武器柜上附加模块来改进。

English: Advanced warp drives have better pentaxid efficiency than standard warp drives.
Chinese (simplified): 33、高级翘曲引擎比标准翘曲引擎具有更好的翘曲晶体效率。

English: You can improve your reputation with a faction you're hostile with by turning in insignias at a bounty office or helping them in combat, mining, or exploration sites.
Chinese (simplified): 34、你可以通过在赏金办公室上交徽章或在战斗、采矿或探索地点帮助他们，来提高与你敌对派系的声望。

English: G, F, and A class stars  are easy difficulty habitable systems.\nM and D class stars are medium difficulty cold systems.\nK, B, and O class stars are hard difficulty hot systems.
Chinese (simplified): G、F和A类恒星是容易难度的适居系统。\nM和D类恒星是中等难度的寒冷系统。\nK、B和O类恒星是高难度的炎热系统。

English: Beware of alien asteroid fields in exotic systems such as black holes or neutron stars.
Chinese (simplified): 36、小心异域星系中的外星小行星场，比如黑洞或中子星。

English: Dangerous enemies can be found at the edge of the galaxy.
Chinese (simplified): 37、在银河系的边缘可以发现危险的敌人。

English: Completing the Project Eden prologue mission introduces you to the UCH Research Vessels and unlocks new missions and progression.
Chinese (simplified): 38、完成伊甸园序章任务将向你介绍UCH研究飞船，并解锁新任务和进展。

English: Advanced devices requiring rare materials cannot be replaced by repair services or repair bays.\nYou must manually replace them if destroyed.
Chinese (simplified): 39、高级设备需要稀有材料，不能通过修理服务或修理舱来替换。\n如果被摧毁，你必须手动替换它们。

English: You can use the search function on the galaxy map to search by planet or star name or by star class.
Chinese (simplified): 40、你可以在银河系地图上使用搜索功能，通过行星或恒星名称或恒星类别进行搜索。

English: Hydroponics bays allow you to harvest the equivalent of 9 crops with a single button press.
Chinese (simplified): 41、水培箱允许你一次收获相当于9单位作物的产量。

English: Solar panels generate passive power based on distance from the main star and planetary atmospheric and weather conditions.
Chinese (simplified): 42、太阳能板根据与主星的距离以及行星的大气和天气条件被动地产生电力。

English: Plasma turbines passively reduce your power consumption at all times.
Chinese (simplified): 43、等离子涡轮机始终被动地减少你的电力消耗。

English: Wind turbines passively reduce your power consumption but can only be used on planets with mild climates.
Chinese (simplified): 44、风力涡轮机可以被动地减少你的电力消耗，但只能在气候温和的行星上使用。

English: Geothermal generators passively reduce your power consumption but can only be used on geologically active planets such as lava planets.
Chinese (simplified): 45、地热发电机可以被动地减少你的电力消耗，但只能在地质活跃的行星上使用，例如熔岩行星。

English: Stealing from your allies or attacking them will lower your reputation.
Chinese (simplified): 46、从你的盟友那里偷窃或攻击他们会降低你的声望。

English: Don't forget to set a home spawn just in case.
Chinese (simplified): 47、别忘了设置一个主重生点以防万一。

English: Many Planets & Moons have untold treasures.  Explore them all. You never know what you'll find!
Chinese (simplified): 48、许多行星和卫星拥有未被发现的宝藏。探索它们所有。你永远不知道会发现什么！

English: Sometimes it's nice to have a place to call home.
Chinese (simplified): 49、有时候，拥有一个可以称之为家的地方很不错。

English: Strange anomalies lurk in the dark.
Chinese (simplified): 50、奇怪的异常现象潜伏在黑暗中。

English: Prey animals are passive and will often run away.\nPredators will attack you on sight.
Chinese (simplified): 51、被捕食动物是被动的，通常会逃跑。食肉动物一旦看到你就会攻击你。

English: Hover vessels can protect you from environmental hazards and hostile wildlife.
Chinese (simplified): 52、悬浮飞飞船可以保护你免受环境危害和敌对野生动植物的威胁。

English: Switch out your armor and armor boosters to fit the situation you find yourself in.
Chinese (simplified): 53、根据你所处的情况，更换你的护甲和护甲增强器。

English: Exotic star systems can contain mystery and danger.
Chinese (simplified): 54、异域星系可能包含神秘和危险。

English: There are dozens of planet and moon types out there to explore.
Chinese (simplified): 55、那里有数十种不同类型的行星和卫星等待你去探索。

English: Trading stations are found in the territory of most major factions.
Chinese (simplified): 56、交易站在大多数主要派系的领土上都能找到。

English: There are places in the galaxy where one must tread carefully.
Chinese (simplified): 57、银河系中有些地方必须小心行事。

English: Some factions are at war with each other and will engage in combat.
Chinese (simplified): 58、一些派系彼此处于战争状态，会进行战斗。

English: Each region has its own color of nebula.
Chinese (simplified): 59、每个区域都有自己的星云颜色。

English: Every star you see is a star you can visit.
Chinese (simplified): 60、你看到的每颗星星都是你可以去访问的星星。

English: Specialized crew offer unique bonuses and further increase your maximum CPU.
Chinese (simplified): 61、专业的船员提供独特的加成，并进一步提高你的最大CPU。

English: Alarm sentries can warn you of approaching danger.
Chinese (simplified): 62、警报哨兵可以警告你即将到来的危险。

English: Don't forget to save a repair template of your ship before going into battle.
Chinese (simplified): 63、别忘了在进入战斗前为你的飞船保存一个修理模板。

English: High-energy laser weapon of The Legacy that is capable of self-aiming through fluctuations in quantum probability that guide it towards a target.\n[c][FF0000]Not for player use[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 遗留者的高能激光武器，它能够利用量子概率的波动来自我瞄准目标。\n[c][FF0000]不供玩家使用[-][/c]

English: Plasma torpedoes explode in proximity to the target afflicting it with active legacy tech that burrows into hull and living things causing permanent, long-lasting mutagenic damage.\n[c][FF0000]Not for player use[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 等离子鱼雷在靠近目标时爆炸，使其受到活跃的遗产科技的影响，这种科技会钻入船体和生物体内，造成永久性的、持久的突变性伤害。\n[c][FF0000]不供玩家使用[-][/c]

English: A Medium weapon pylon for mounting different bomb types for use against enemy fortifications.\n[c][00FF00]No Reload Delay\nUse RMB to select different variants[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一种中型武器挂架，用于安装不同类型的炸弹，以对抗敌人的防御工事。\n[c][00FF00]无装填延迟\n使用右键点击（RMB）选择不同形态[-][/c]

English: Block group for legacy-only devices and technology intended for POI use only. Cannot be retrieved.\n[c][FF0000]NOT FOR PLAYER USE[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 仅用于遗留者设备的方块组，以及仅用于兴趣点的技术。无法回收。\n[c][FF0000]不供玩家使用[-][/c]

English: Adjustable shell cover for Legacy Ships and POIs. Is placed in OFF mode. Up to 5 turrets can be placed inside the block to make them easier to see and hit as a group target.\nBioshell will always be destroyed first when shot at and will explode destroying everything contained within it.\nTurning the Bioshell on in the control panel will give it an alternating shield like the ProtoInfector boss.
Chinese (simplified): 可调节的外壳覆盖，用于遗留者飞船和兴趣点（POI）。目前处于关闭模式。可以在该方块内放置多达5个炮塔，使它们更容易作为一个组目标被看到和击中。\n当被射击时，生物壳始终会首先被摧毁，并在爆炸时摧毁其内部包含的所有物品。\n在控制面板上打开生物壳将为其提供一种与原型感染者（ProtoInfector）boss相似的交替护盾。

English: Polaris' signature high-strength, long-ranged spotlights capable of lighting up objects a long distance away on even the darkest of planets with the thickest of atmospheres.
Chinese (simplified): 北极星的标志性高强度、长距离聚光灯，即使在最黑暗的星球上，即使大气层最厚，也能照亮远处的物体。

English: A dedicated terminal used for uploading software updates for weapons and turrets on a connected network.\n[c][00FF00]Uses Software Updates to improve weapons and systems for the ship you are currently piloting[-][/c]
Chinese (simplified): 一个专用终端，用于在连接的网络上为武器和炮塔上传软件更新。\n[c][00FF00]使用软件更新来改进你当前驾驶的飞船的武器和系统[-][/c]

English: Search for playfield name (partial match) or star type (exact match)\nSee the Galaxy section of the Empyiopedia [c][ffff00](F1)[-][/c] for help
Italiano: Cerca una Stella o un Pianeta
Portuguese (Euro): Procura uma estrela ou um planeta
Chinese (simplified): 搜索游戏场地名称（部分匹配）或恒星类型（完全匹配）\n请参阅Empyriopedia的银河部分 [c][ffff00](F1)[-][/c] 以获取帮助。
Greek: Αναζήτησε για ένα αστέρι ή πλανήτη
Vietnamese: Tìm kiếm ngôi sao hoặc hành tinh

English: Micro Jump Drives can be used to quickly traverse a sector.
Chinese (simplified): 短程跳跃驱动器可以用来快速穿越一个星区。
